",\"tag 96\",\"password\",\"HMAC\",\"FIX session\"],\"href\":\"/exchange/guides/fix/authentication\"}]},{\"group\":\"Integration\",\"public\":true,\"pages\":[{\"title\":\"Spot REST Introduction\",\"sidebarTitle\":\"REST overview\",\"description\":\"Overview of the Kraken Spot REST API organisation, requests, responses, and error handling\",\"href\":\"/exchange/guides/rest/introduction\"},{\"title\":\"Spot WebSocket Introduction\",\"sidebarTitle\":\"WebSocket overview\",\"description\":\"WebSocket v1 and v2 endpoints, connection details, version differences, and general considerations for the Spot WebSocket API\",\"keywords\":[\"WebSocket\",\"wss\",\"v1\",\"v2\",\"real-time\",\"subscription\",\"channel\",\"ping\",\"reconnect\"],\"href\":\"/exchange/guides/websockets/introduction\"},{\"title\":\"FIX Introduction\",\"sidebarTitle\":\"FIX overview\",\"description\":\"Overview of the Kraken FIX 4.4 API — session architecture, supported messages, connectivity, and key design considerations\",\"href\":\"/exchange/guides/fix/introduction\"},{\"title\":\"Order lifecycle\",\"description\":\"Every order state, transition, and how to observe them across REST, WebSocket, and FIX\",\"href\":\"/exchange/guides/general/order-lifecycle\"},{\"title\":\"Error messages\",\"description\":\"All error codes returned by the Kraken Spot REST API, organized by category, with causes and handling guidance\",\"href\":\"/exchange/guides/general/errors\"},{\"title\":\"Spot Trading Limits\",\"sidebarTitle\":\"Trading limits\",\"description\":\"Per-pair rate counters, decay rates, and open order limits enforced by the Spot trading engine across REST, WebSocket, and FIX\",\"keywords\":[\"rate limit\",\"trading limits\",\"rate counter\",\"order limit\",\"throttle\",\"EOrder:Rate limit exceeded\"],\"href\":\"/exchange/guides/general/ratelimits\"}]},{\"group\":\"Futures\",\"public\":true,\"pages\":[{\"title\":\"Derivatives Introduction\",\"sidebarTitle\":\"Introduction\",\"description\":\"Overview of the Kraken Derivatives (Futures) API — REST, WebSocket, and FIX access, conventions, and testing environment\",\"href\":\"/exchange/guides/futures/introduction\"},{\"title\":\"Derivatives REST\",\"sidebarTitle\":\"REST\",\"description\":\"Authentication, request format, and response structure for the Derivatives REST API\",\"href\":\"/exchange/guides/futures/rest\"},{\"title\":\"Derivatives WebSocket\",\"sidebarTitle\":\"WebSocket\",\"description\":\"Authentication, subscriptions, and real-time feeds for the Kraken Derivatives WebSocket API\",\"href\":\"/exchange/guides/futures/websockets\"},{\"title\":\"Derivatives Rate Limits\",\"sidebarTitle\":\"Rate limits\",\"description\":\"Request cost budgets and WebSocket connection limits for the Derivatives REST and WebSocket APIs\",\"keywords\":[\"rate limit\",\"throttling\",\"derivatives\",\"futures\",\"request cost\",\"api limit exceeded\"],\"href\":\"/exchange/guides/futures/ratelimits\"}]},{\"group\":\"Production\",\"public\":true,\"pages\":[{\"title\":\"Reconnection and resilience\",\"sidebarTitle\":\"Reconnection\",\"description\":\"How to handle WebSocket disconnections, re-subscription, and state reconciliation\",\"href\":\"/exchange/guides/websockets/reconnection\"},{\"title\":\"Colocation and connectivity\",\"description\":\"Low-latency connectivity options for Kraken's trading infrastructure, from cloud to direct cross-connect\",\"href\":\"/exchange/guides/general/colocation\"},{\"title\":\"Sub-accounts and multi-account management\",\"sidebarTitle\":\"Sub-accounts\",\"description\":\"How to structure and operate multiple accounts via the API — sub-account creation, fund transfers, and FIX broker management\",\"href\":\"/exchange/guides/general/subaccounts\"}]},{\"group\":\"Advanced\",\"public\":true,\"pages\":[{\"title\":\"Historical data\",\"description\":\"How to access OHLCV history, trade ticks, and order book snapshots for backtesting and research\",\"href\":\"/exchange/guides/general/historical-data\"},{\"title\":\"Spot REST Rate Limits\",\"sidebarTitle\":\"REST rate limits\",\"description\":\"REST API call counter, tier-based limits and decay rates, and matching engine limits that apply across all Spot protocols\",\"keywords\":[\"rate limit\",\"REST\",\"call counter\",\"throttle\",\"tier\",\"decay\",\"EAPI:Rate limit exceeded\"],\"href\":\"/exchange/guides/rest/ratelimits\"},{\"title\":\"Spot REST Earn\",\"sidebarTitle\":\"Earn\",\"description\":\"How to allocate and deallocate funds to Kraken Earn strategies, check allocation status, and understand geo restrictions\",\"keywords\":[\"earn\",\"staking\",\"yield\",\"allocate\",\"deallocate\",\"strategies\",\"rewards\",\"bonding\"],\"href\":\"/exchange/guides/rest/earn\"},{\"title\":\"Spot Atomic Amends\",\"sidebarTitle\":\"Order amends\",\"description\":\"How atomic amends work, how they differ from legacy edit transactions, and which fields can be modified in-place without losing queue priority\",\"keywords\":[\"amend order\",\"atomic amend\",\"edit order\",\"cancel replace\",\"queue priority\",\"cl_ord_id\",\"AmendOrder\"],\"href\":\"/exchange/guides/general/amends\"},{\"title\":\"Spot Client Order Identifiers\",\"sidebarTitle\":\"Client order IDs\",\"description\":\"How to use cl_ord_id — client-assigned order identifiers — to track and manage orders across REST, WebSocket, and FIX\",\"keywords\":[\"cl_ord_id\",\"client order ID\",\"ClOrdID\",\"order identifier\",\"userref\",\"UUID\",\"FIX tag 11\"],\"href\":\"/exchange/guides/general/clordid\"},{\"title\":\"Spot Level 3 Market Data\",\"sidebarTitle\":\"L3 market data\",\"description\":\"Individual order visibility in the Kraken order book — queue priority, fill probability, and how to access L3 data via WebSocket, FIX, and REST\",\"keywords\":[\"L3\",\"level 3\",\"order book\",\"queue priority\",\"order ID\",\"level3 channel\",\"FIX port 4005\"],\"href\":\"/exchange/guides/general/l3-data\"},{\"title\":\"Book checksum (WebSocket v2)\",\"sidebarTitle\":\"Book checksum (v2)\",\"description\":\"How to maintain the order book and validate the CRC32 checksum on the WebSocket v2 book channel\",\"href\":\"/exchange/guides/websockets/book-checksum-v2\"},{\"title\":\"L3 checksum (WebSocket v2)\",\"sidebarTitle\":\"L3 checksum (v2)\",\"description\":\"How to maintain the level3 order book and validate the CRC32 checksum on the WebSocket v2 level3 channel\",\"href\":\"/exchange/guides/websockets/l3-checksum-v2\"},{\"title\":\"Book checksum (WebSocket v1)\",\"sidebarTitle\":\"Book checksum (v1)\",\"description\":\"How to maintain the order book and validate the CRC32 checksum on the WebSocket v1 book channel\",\"href\":\"/exchange/guides/websockets/book-checksum-v1\"},{\"title\":\"Book checksum (FIX)\",\"sidebarTitle\":\"Book checksum (FIX)\",\"description\":\"How to maintain the order book and validate the CRC32 checksum on the FIX Market Data Incremental Refresh\",\"href\":\"/exchange/guides/fix/checksums\"},{\"title\":\"Spot Example Clients\",\"sidebarTitle\":\"Example clients\",\"description\":\"Community and official API client libraries for Spot REST and WebSocket in Python, Go, Java, and more\",\"keywords\":[\"SDK\",\"client library\",\"python\",\"go\",\"java\",\"rust\",\"example\",\"sample code\"],\"href\":\"/exchange/guides/general/examples\"}]}]},{\"tab\":\"API Reference\",\"dropdowns\":[{\"dropdown\":\"Overview\",\"icon\":\"compass\",\"pages\":[{\"title\":\"Exchange API reference\",\"sidebarTitle\":\"Overview\",\"description\":\"Choose a protocol — REST, WebSocket, or FIX — for Spot or Derivatives trading\",\"public\":true,\"href\":\"/exchange/api-reference/overview\"}]},{\"dropdown\":\"Spot REST\",\"icon\":\"code\",\"groups\":[{\"group\":\"Market Data\",\"public\":true,\"pages\":[{\"title\":\"Get Server Time\",\"description\":\"Get the server's time.\\n\",\"deprecated\":null,\"version\":null,\"openapi\":\"/openapi/spot-rest.yaml get /public/Time\",\"href\":\"/api-reference/market-data/get-server-time\",\"autogeneratedByOpenApi\":true},{\"title\":\"Get System Status\",\"description\":\"Get the current system status or trading mode.\\n\",\"deprecated\":null,\"version\":null,\"openapi\":\"/openapi/spot-rest.yaml get /public/SystemStatus\",\"href\":\"/api-reference/market-data/get-system-status\",\"autogeneratedByOpenApi\":true},{\"title\":\"Get Asset Info\",\"description\":\"Get information about the assets that are available for deposit, withdrawal, trading and earn.\\n\",\"deprecated\":null,\"version\":null,\"openapi\":\"/openapi/spot-rest.yaml get /public/Assets\",\"href\":\"/api-reference/market-data/get-asset-info\",\"autogeneratedByOpenApi\":true},{\"title\":\"Get Tradable Asset Pairs\",\"description\":\"Get tradable asset pairs\\n\",\"deprecated\":null,\"version\":null,\"openapi\":\"/openapi/spot-rest.yaml get /public/AssetPairs\",\"href\":\"/api-reference/market-data/get-tradable-asset-pairs\",\"autogeneratedByOpenApi\":true},{\"title\":\"Get Ticker Information\",\"description\":\"Get ticker information for all or requested markets. To clarify usage, note that \\n* Today's prices start at midnight UTC\\n* Leaving the pair parameter blank will return tickers for all tradeable assets on Kraken\\n\",\"deprecated\":null,\"version\":null,\"openapi\":\"/openapi/spot-rest.yaml get /public/Ticker\",\"href\":\"/api-reference/market-data/get-ticker-information\",\"autogeneratedByOpenApi\":true},{\"title\":\"Get OHLC Data\",\"description\":\"Retrieve OHLC market data.\\nThe last entry in the OHLC array is for the current, not-yet-committed timeframe, and will always be present, regardless of the value of `since`.\\nReturns up to 720 of the most recent entries (older data cannot be retrieved, regardless of the value of `since`).\\n\",\"deprecated\":null,\"version\":null,\"openapi\":\"/openapi/spot-rest.yaml get /public/OHLC\",\"href\":\"/api-reference/market-data/get-ohlc-data\",\"autogeneratedByOpenApi\":true},{\"title\":\"Get Order Book\",\"description\":\"Returns level 2 (L2) order book, which describes the individual price levels in the book with aggregated order quantities at each level.\\n\",\"deprecated\":null,\"version\":null,\"openapi\":\"/openapi/spot-rest.yaml get /public/Depth\",\"href\":\"/api-reference/market-data/get-order-book\",\"autogeneratedByOpenApi\":true},{\"title\":\"Query L3 Order Book\",\"description\":\"Retrieve Level3 order book data, which provides individual order information at each price level.\\nThis includes order IDs and timestamps for each order in the book. \\n\\nThe Level3 endpoint requires authentication.\\n\\n**API Key Permissions Required:** `Orders and trades - Query open orders \u0026 trades`\\n\",\"deprecated\":null,\"version\":null,\"openapi\":\"/openapi/spot-rest.yaml post /private/Level3\",\"href\":\"/api-reference/market-data/query-l3-order-book\",\"autogeneratedByOpenApi\":true},{\"title\":\"Get Grouped Order Book\",\"description\":\"The GroupedBook endpoint aggregates the volume in the order book over a specified tick range. \\nIt provides a summary of liquidity deep into the book, useful for user interface display.\\n\\nBids and asks between grouped price levels are accumulated to the nearest passive level (asks rounded up, bids down).\\n\",\"deprecated\":null,\"version\":null,\"openapi\":\"/openapi/spot-rest.yaml get /public/GroupedBook\",\"href\":\"/api-reference/market-data/get-grouped-order-book\",\"autogeneratedByOpenApi\":true},{\"title\":\"Get Recent Trades\",\"description\":\"Returns the last 1000 trades by default\\n\",\"deprecated\":null,\"version\":null,\"openapi\":\"/openapi/spot-rest.yaml get /public/Trades\",\"href\":\"/api-reference/market-data/get-recent-trades\",\"autogeneratedByOpenApi\":true},{\"title\":\"Get Recent Spreads\",\"description\":\"Returns the last ~200 top-of-book spreads for a given pair\\n\",\"deprecated\":null,\"version\":null,\"openapi\":\"/openapi/spot-rest.yaml get /public/Spread\",\"href\":\"/api-reference/market-data/get-recent-spreads\",\"autogeneratedByOpenApi\":true}]},{\"group\":\"Account Data\",\"public\":true,\"pages\":[{\"title\":\"Get Account Balance\",\"description\":\"Retrieve all cash balances, net of pending withdrawals.\\n\\n**Note on Staking/Earn assets:** We have begun to migrate assets from our legacy Staking system over to a new Earn system. As such, the following assets may appear in your balances and ledger. Please see our [Support article](https://support.kraken.com/hc/en-us/articles/360039879471-What-is-Asset-S-and-Asset-M-) for more details. Note that these assets are \\\"read-only\\\", to interact with your balances in them please use the base asset (e.g. `USDT` to transact with your `USDT` and `USDT.F` balances).\\n\\n**Symbol Extensions**:\\n* `.B`: balances in new yield-bearing products, similar to `.S` (staked) and `.M` (opt-in rewards) balances\\n* `.F`: balances earning automatically in Kraken Rewards\\n* `.T`: tokenized assets.\\n\\n**API Key Permissions Required:** `Funds permissions - Query`\\n\",\"deprecated\":null,\"version\":null,\"openapi\":\"/openapi/spot-rest.yaml post /private/Balance\",\"href\":\"/api-reference/account-data/get-account-balance\",\"autogeneratedByOpenApi\":true},{\"title\":\"Get Extended Balance\",\"description\":\"$34\",\"deprecated\":null,\"version\":null,\"openapi\":\"/openapi/spot-rest.yaml post /private/BalanceEx\",\"href\":\"/api-reference/account-data/get-extended-balance\",\"autogeneratedByOpenApi\":true},{\"title\":\"Get Credit Lines\",\"description\":\"Retrieve all credit line details for VIPs with this functionality.\\n\\n**API Key Permissions Required:** `Funds permissions - Query`\\n\",\"deprecated\":null,\"version\":null,\"openapi\":\"/openapi/spot-rest.yaml post /private/CreditLines\",\"href\":\"/api-reference/account-data/get-credit-lines\",\"autogeneratedByOpenApi\":true},{\"title\":\"Get Trade Balance\",\"description\":\"Retrieve a summary of collateral balances, margin position valuations, equity and margin level.\\n\\n**API Key Permissions Required:** `Orders and trades - Query open orders \u0026 trades`\\n\",\"deprecated\":null,\"version\":null,\"openapi\":\"/openapi/spot-rest.yaml post /private/TradeBalance\",\"href\":\"/api-reference/account-data/get-trade-balance\",\"autogeneratedByOpenApi\":true},{\"title\":\"Get Open Orders\",\"description\":\"Retrieve information about currently open orders.\\n\\n**API Key Permissions Required:** `Orders and trades - Query open orders \u0026 trades`\\n\",\"deprecated\":null,\"version\":null,\"openapi\":\"/openapi/spot-rest.yaml post /private/OpenOrders\",\"href\":\"/api-reference/account-data/get-open-orders\",\"autogeneratedByOpenApi\":true},{\"title\":\"Get Closed Orders\",\"description\":\"Retrieve information about orders that have been closed (filled or cancelled). 50 results are returned at a time, the most recent by default.\\n\\n**Note:** If an order's tx ID is given for `start` or `end` time, the order's opening time (`opentm`) is used\\n\\n**API Key Permissions Required:** `Orders and trades - Query closed orders \u0026 trades`\\n\",\"deprecated\":null,\"version\":null,\"openapi\":\"/openapi/spot-rest.yaml post /private/ClosedOrders\",\"href\":\"/api-reference/account-data/get-closed-orders\",\"autogeneratedByOpenApi\":true},{\"title\":\"Query Orders Info\",\"description\":\"Retrieve information about specific orders.\\n\\n**API Key Permissions Required:** `Orders and trades - Query open orders \u0026 trades` or `Orders and trades - Query closed orders \u0026 trades`, depending on status of order\\n\",\"deprecated\":null,\"version\":null,\"openapi\":\"/openapi/spot-rest.yaml post /private/QueryOrders\",\"href\":\"/api-reference/account-data/query-orders-info\",\"autogeneratedByOpenApi\":true},{\"title\":\"Get Order Amends\",\"description\":\"Retrieves an audit trail of amend transactions on the specified order. The list is ordered by ascending amend timestamp.\\n\\n**API Key Permissions Required:** `Orders and trades - Query open orders \u0026 trades` or `Orders and trades - Query closed orders \u0026 trades`, depending on status of order.\\n\",\"deprecated\":null,\"version\":null,\"openapi\":\"/openapi/spot-rest.yaml post /private/OrderAmends\",\"href\":\"/api-reference/account-data/get-order-amends\",\"autogeneratedByOpenApi\":true},{\"title\":\"Get Trades History\",\"description\":\"Retrieve information about trades/fills. 50 results are returned at a time, the most recent by default.\\n* Unless otherwise stated, costs, fees, prices, and volumes are specified with the precision for the asset pair (`pair_decimals` and `lot_decimals`), not the individual assets' precision (`decimals`).\\n\\n**API Key Permissions Required:** `Orders and trades - Query closed orders \u0026 trades`\\n\",\"deprecated\":null,\"version\":null,\"openapi\":\"/openapi/spot-rest.yaml post /private/TradesHistory\",\"href\":\"/api-reference/account-data/get-trades-history\",\"autogeneratedByOpenApi\":true},{\"title\":\"Query Trades Info\",\"description\":\"Retrieve information about specific trades/fills.\\n\\n**API Key Permissions Required:** `Orders and trades - Query closed orders \u0026 trades`\\n\",\"deprecated\":null,\"version\":null,\"openapi\":\"/openapi/spot-rest.yaml post /private/QueryTrades\",\"href\":\"/api-reference/account-data/query-trades-info\",\"autogeneratedByOpenApi\":true},{\"title\":\"Get Open Positions\",\"description\":\"Get information about open margin positions.\\n\\n**API Key Permissions Required:** `Orders and trades - Query open orders \u0026 trades`\\n\",\"deprecated\":null,\"version\":null,\"openapi\":\"/openapi/spot-rest.yaml post /private/OpenPositions\",\"href\":\"/api-reference/account-data/get-open-positions\",\"autogeneratedByOpenApi\":true},{\"title\":\"Get Ledgers Info\",\"description\":\"Retrieve information about ledger entries. 50 results are returned at a time, the most recent by default.\\n\\n\u003e **Note on Staking/Earn assets:** We have begun to migrate assets from our legacy Staking system over to a new Earn system. As such, the following assets may appear in your balances and ledger. Please see our [Support article](https://support.kraken.com/hc/en-us/articles/360039879471-What-is-Asset-S-and-Asset-M-) for more details. Note that these assets are \\\"read-only\\\", to interact with your balances in them please use the base asset (e.g. `USDT` to transact with your `USDT` and `USDT.F` balances).\\n\u003e * `.B`, which represents balances in new yield-bearing products, similar to `.S` (staked) and `.M` (opt-in rewards) balances\\n\u003e * `.F`, which represents balances earning automatically in Kraken Rewards\\n\\n**API Key Permissions Required:** `Data - Query ledger entries`\\n\",\"deprecated\":null,\"version\":null,\"openapi\":\"/openapi/spot-rest.yaml post /private/Ledgers\",\"href\":\"/api-reference/account-data/get-ledgers-info\",\"autogeneratedByOpenApi\":true},{\"title\":\"Query Ledgers\",\"description\":\"Retrieve information about specific ledger entries. \\n\\n\u003e **Note on Staking/Earn assets:** We have begun to migrate assets from our legacy Staking system over to a new Earn system. As such, the following assets may appear in your balances and ledger. Please see our [Support article](https://support.kraken.com/hc/en-us/articles/360039879471-What-is-Asset-S-and-Asset-M-) for more details. Note that these assets are \\\"read-only\\\", to interact with your balances in them please use the base asset (e.g. `USDT` to transact with your `USDT` and `USDT.F` balances).\\n\u003e * `.B`, which represents balances in new yield-bearing products, similar to `.S` (staked) and `.M` (opt-in rewards) balances\\n\u003e * `.F`, which represents balances earning automatically in Kraken Rewards\\n\\n**API Key Permissions Required:** `Data - Query ledger entries`\\n\",\"deprecated\":null,\"version\":null,\"openapi\":\"/openapi/spot-rest.yaml post /private/QueryLedgers\",\"href\":\"/api-reference/account-data/query-ledgers\",\"autogeneratedByOpenApi\":true},{\"title\":\"Get Trade Volume\",\"description\":\"Returns 30 day USD trading volume and resulting fee schedule for any asset pair(s) provided. Fees will not be included if `pair` is not specified as Kraken fees differ by asset pair.\\nNote: If an asset pair is on a maker/taker fee schedule, the taker side is given in `fees` and maker side in `fees_maker`. For pairs not on maker/taker, they will only be given in `fees`.\\n\\n`pair` accepts either a comma-delimited list of pair names or a list of `{ asset, aclass }` objects (the latter is required for non-forex classes such as `derivatives` or `equity_pair`). Set `fee_schedule` to `true` to additionally receive the full fee schedule per trading pair in the `schedules` field.\\n\\n**API Key Permissions Required:** `Funds permissions - Query`\\n\",\"deprecated\":null,\"version\":null,\"openapi\":\"/openapi/spot-rest.yaml post /private/TradeVolume\",\"href\":\"/api-reference/account-data/get-trade-volume\",\"autogeneratedByOpenApi\":true},{\"title\":\"Request Export Report\",\"description\":\"Request export of trades or ledgers.\\n\\n**API Key Permissions Required:** `Data - Export data`\\n\",\"deprecated\":null,\"version\":null,\"openapi\":\"/openapi/spot-rest.yaml post /private/AddExport\",\"href\":\"/api-reference/account-data/request-export-report\",\"autogeneratedByOpenApi\":true},{\"title\":\"Get Export Report Status\",\"description\":\"Get status of requested data exports.\\n\\n**API Key Permissions Required:** `Data - Export data`\\n\",\"deprecated\":null,\"version\":null,\"openapi\":\"/openapi/spot-rest.yaml post /private/ExportStatus\",\"href\":\"/api-reference/account-data/get-export-report-status\",\"autogeneratedByOpenApi\":true},{\"title\":\"Retrieve Data Export\",\"description\":\"Retrieve a processed data export \\n\\n**API Key Permissions Required:** `Data - Export data`\\n\",\"deprecated\":null,\"version\":null,\"openapi\":\"/openapi/spot-rest.yaml post /private/RetrieveExport\",\"href\":\"/api-reference/account-data/retrieve-data-export\",\"autogeneratedByOpenApi\":true},{\"title\":\"Delete Export Report\",\"description\":\"Delete exported trades/ledgers report\\n\\n**API Key Permissions Required:** `Data - Export data`\\n\",\"deprecated\":null,\"version\":null,\"openapi\":\"/openapi/spot-rest.yaml post /private/RemoveExport\",\"href\":\"/api-reference/account-data/delete-export-report\",\"autogeneratedByOpenApi\":true},{\"title\":\"Get API Key Info\",\"description\":\"Retrieve information about the API key that is used to make the request, including its name, permissions, restrictions, and usage timestamps.\\n\\n**API Key Permissions Required:** `None`\\n\",\"deprecated\":null,\"version\":null,\"openapi\":\"/openapi/spot-rest.yaml post /private/GetApiKeyInfo\",\"href\":\"/api-reference/account-data/get-api-key-info\",\"autogeneratedByOpenApi\":true}]},{\"group\":\"Trading\",\"public\":true,\"pages\":[{\"title\":\"Add Order\",\"description\":\"Place a new order.\\n\\n**Note**: See the [AssetPairs](/docs/rest-api/get-tradable-asset-pairs) endpoint for details on the available trading pairs, their price and quantity precisions, order minimums, available leverage, etc.\\n\\n**API Key Permissions Required:** `Orders and trades - Create \u0026 modify orders`\\n\",\"deprecated\":null,\"version\":null,\"openapi\":\"/openapi/spot-rest.yaml post /private/AddOrder\",\"href\":\"/api-reference/trading/add-order\",\"autogeneratedByOpenApi\":true},{\"title\":\"Amend Order\",\"description\":\"The amend request enables clients to modify the order parameters in-place without the need to cancel the existing order and create a new one.\\n\\n* The order identifiers assigned by Kraken and/or client will stay the same.\\n* Queue priority in the order book will be maintained where possible. \\n* If an amend request will reduce the order quantity below the existing filled quantity, the remaining quantity will be cancelled.\\n\\nFor more detail, see [amend transaction guide](/docs/guides/spot-amends).\\n\\n**API Key Permissions Required:** `Orders and trades - Create \u0026 modify orders` or `Orders and trades - Cancel \u0026 close orders`\\n\",\"deprecated\":null,\"version\":null,\"openapi\":\"/openapi/spot-rest.yaml post /private/AmendOrder\",\"href\":\"/api-reference/trading/amend-order\",\"autogeneratedByOpenApi\":true},{\"title\":\"Edit Order\",\"description\":\"Sends a request to edit the order parameters of a live order. When an order has been successfully modified, the original order will be cancelled and a new order will be \\ncreated with the adjusted parameters a new `txid` will be returned in the response.\\n\\n**Note:** The new [AmendOrder](/exchange/guides/general/amends) endpoint resolves the caveats listed below and has additional performance gains.\\n\\nCaveats for `EditOrder`:\\n* Triggered stop loss or take profit orders are not supported.\\n* Orders with conditional close terms attached are not supported.\\n* Orders where the executed volume is greater than the newly supplied volume will be rejected.\\n* `cl_ord_id` is not supported.\\n* Existing executions are associated with the original order and not copied to the amended order.\\n* Queue position will not be maintained.\\n\\n**API Key Permissions Required:** `Orders and trades - Create \u0026 modify orders` and `Orders and trades - Cancel \u0026 close orders`\\n\",\"deprecated\":null,\"version\":null,\"openapi\":\"/openapi/spot-rest.yaml post /private/EditOrder\",\"href\":\"/api-reference/trading/edit-order\",\"autogeneratedByOpenApi\":true},{\"title\":\"Cancel Order\",\"description\":\"Cancel a particular open order (or set of open orders) by `txid`, `userref` or `cl_ord_id`\\n\\n**API Key Permissions Required:** `Orders and trades - Create \u0026 modify orders` or `Orders and trades - Cancel \u0026 close orders`\\n\",\"deprecated\":null,\"version\":null,\"openapi\":\"/openapi/spot-rest.yaml post /private/CancelOrder\",\"href\":\"/api-reference/trading/cancel-order\",\"autogeneratedByOpenApi\":true},{\"title\":\"Cancel All Orders\",\"description\":\"Cancel all open orders\\n\\n**API Key Permissions Required:** `Orders and trades - Create \u0026 modify orders` or `Orders and trades - Cancel \u0026 close orders`\\n\",\"deprecated\":null,\"version\":null,\"openapi\":\"/openapi/spot-rest.yaml post /private/CancelAll\",\"href\":\"/api-reference/trading/cancel-all-orders\",\"autogeneratedByOpenApi\":true},{\"title\":\"Cancel All Orders After X\",\"description\":\"$35\",\"deprecated\":null,\"version\":null,\"openapi\":\"/openapi/spot-rest.yaml post /private/CancelAllOrdersAfter\",\"href\":\"/api-reference/trading/cancel-all-orders-after-x\",\"autogeneratedByOpenApi\":true},{\"title\":\"Add Order Batch\",\"description\":\"Sends a collection of orders (minimum of 2 and maximum 15): \\n* Validation is performed on the whole batch prior to submission to the engine. If an order fails validation, the whole batch will be rejected.\\n* On submission to the engine, if an order fails pre-match checks (i.e. funding), then the individual order will be rejected and remainder of the batch will be processed. \\n* All orders in batch are limited to a single pair.\\n\\n**Note**: See the [AssetPairs](/docs/rest-api/get-tradable-asset-pairs) endpoint for details on the available trading pairs, their price and quantity precisions, order minimums, available leverage, etc.\\n\\n**API Key Permissions Required:** `Orders and trades - Create \u0026 modify orders` and `Orders and trades - Cancel \u0026 close orders`\\n\",\"deprecated\":null,\"version\":null,\"openapi\":\"/openapi/spot-rest.yaml post /private/AddOrderBatch\",\"href\":\"/api-reference/trading/add-order-batch\",\"autogeneratedByOpenApi\":true},{\"title\":\"Cancel Order Batch\",\"description\":\"Cancel multiple open orders  by `txid`, `userref` or `cl_ord_id`(maximum 50 total unique IDs/references)\\n\\n**API Key Permissions Required:** `Orders and trades - Create \u0026 modify orders` or `Orders and trades - Cancel \u0026 close orders`\\n\",\"deprecated\":null,\"version\":null,\"openapi\":\"/openapi/spot-rest.yaml post /private/CancelOrderBatch\",\"href\":\"/api-reference/trading/cancel-order-batch\",\"autogeneratedByOpenApi\":true},{\"title\":\"Get Websockets Token\",\"description\":\"An authentication token must be requested via this REST API endpoint in order to connect to and authenticate with our [Websockets API](../guides/spot-ws-auth). The token should be used within 15 minutes of creation, but it does not expire once a successful Websockets connection and private subscription has been made and is maintained.\\n\\n**API Key Permissions Required:** `WebSocket interface - On`\\n\",\"deprecated\":null,\"version\":null,\"openapi\":\"/openapi/spot-rest.yaml post /private/GetWebSocketsToken\",\"href\":\"/api-reference/trading/get-websockets-token\",\"autogeneratedByOpenApi\":true}]},{\"group\":\"Funding\",\"public\":true,\"pages\":[{\"title\":\"Get Deposit Methods\",\"description\":\"Retrieve methods available for depositing a particular asset.\\n\\n**API Key Permissions Required:** `Funds permissions - Query` and `Funds permissions - Deposit`\\n\",\"deprecated\":null,\"version\":null,\"openapi\":\"/openapi/spot-rest.yaml post /private/DepositMethods\",\"href\":\"/api-reference/funding/get-deposit-methods\",\"autogeneratedByOpenApi\":true},{\"title\":\"Get Deposit Addresses\",\"description\":\"Retrieve (or generate a new) deposit addresses for a particular asset and method.\\n\\n**API Key Permissions Required:** `Funds permissions - Query`\\n\",\"deprecated\":null,\"version\":null,\"openapi\":\"/openapi/spot-rest.yaml post /private/DepositAddresses\",\"href\":\"/api-reference/funding/get-deposit-addresses\",\"autogeneratedByOpenApi\":true},{\"title\":\"Get Status of Recent Deposits\",\"description\":\"Retrieve information about recent deposits. Results are sorted by recency, use the `cursor` parameter to iterate through list of deposits (page size equal to value of `limit`) from newest to oldest.\\n**API Key Permissions Required:** `Funds permissions - Query`\\n\",\"deprecated\":null,\"version\":null,\"openapi\":\"/openapi/spot-rest.yaml post /private/DepositStatus\",\"href\":\"/api-reference/funding/get-status-of-recent-deposits\",\"autogeneratedByOpenApi\":true},{\"title\":\"Get Withdrawal Methods\",\"description\":\"Retrieve a list of withdrawal methods available for the user.\\n\\n**API Key Permissions Required:** `Funds permissions - Query` and `Funds permissions - Withdraw`\\n\",\"deprecated\":null,\"version\":null,\"openapi\":\"/openapi/spot-rest.yaml post /private/WithdrawMethods\",\"href\":\"/api-reference/funding/get-withdrawal-methods\",\"autogeneratedByOpenApi\":true},{\"title\":\"Get Withdrawal Addresses\",\"description\":\"Retrieve a list of withdrawal addresses available for the user.\\n\\n**API Key Permissions Required:** `Funds permissions - Query` and `Funds permissions - Withdraw`\\n\",\"deprecated\":null,\"version\":null,\"openapi\":\"/openapi/spot-rest.yaml post /private/WithdrawAddresses\",\"href\":\"/api-reference/funding/get-withdrawal-addresses\",\"autogeneratedByOpenApi\":true},{\"title\":\"Get Withdrawal Information\",\"description\":\"Retrieve fee information about potential withdrawals for a particular asset, key and amount.\\n\\n**API Key Permissions Required:** `Funds permissions - Query` and `Funds permissions - Withdraw`\\n\",\"deprecated\":null,\"version\":null,\"openapi\":\"/openapi/spot-rest.yaml post /private/WithdrawInfo\",\"href\":\"/api-reference/funding/get-withdrawal-information\",\"autogeneratedByOpenApi\":true},{\"title\":\"Withdraw Funds\",\"description\":\"Make a withdrawal request.    \\n\\n**API Key Permissions Required:** `Funds permissions - Withdraw`\\n\",\"deprecated\":null,\"version\":null,\"openapi\":\"/openapi/spot-rest.yaml post /private/Withdraw\",\"href\":\"/api-reference/funding/withdraw-funds\",\"autogeneratedByOpenApi\":true},{\"title\":\"Get Status of Recent Withdrawals\",\"description\":\"Retrieve information about recent withdrawals. Results are sorted by recency, use the `cursor` parameter to iterate through list of withdrawals (page size equal to value of `limit`) from newest to oldest.\\n\\n**API Key Permissions Required:** `Funds permissions - Withdraw` or `Data - Query ledger entries`\\n\",\"deprecated\":null,\"version\":null,\"openapi\":\"/openapi/spot-rest.yaml post /private/WithdrawStatus\",\"href\":\"/api-reference/funding/get-status-of-recent-withdrawals\",\"autogeneratedByOpenApi\":true},{\"title\":\"Request Withdrawal Cancellation\",\"description\":\"Cancel a recently requested withdrawal, if it has not already been successfully processed.\\n\\n**API Key Permissions Required:** `Funds permissions - Withdraw`, unless withdrawal is a `WalletTransfer`, then no permissions are required.\\n\",\"deprecated\":null,\"version\":null,\"openapi\":\"/openapi/spot-rest.yaml post /private/WithdrawCancel\",\"href\":\"/api-reference/funding/request-withdrawal-cancellation\",\"autogeneratedByOpenApi\":true},{\"title\":\"Request Wallet Transfer\",\"description\":\"Transfer from a Kraken spot wallet to a Kraken Futures wallet. Note that a transfer in the other direction must be requested via the Kraken Futures API endpoint for [withdrawals to Spot wallets](../futures-api/trading/withdrawal).\\n\\n**API Key Permissions Required:** `Funds permissions - Query`\\n\",\"deprecated\":null,\"version\":null,\"openapi\":\"/openapi/spot-rest.yaml post /private/WalletTransfer\",\"href\":\"/api-reference/funding/request-wallet-transfer\",\"autogeneratedByOpenApi\":true}]},{\"group\":\"Subaccounts\",\"public\":true,\"pages\":[{\"title\":\"Create Subaccount\",\"description\":\"Create a trading subaccount. **Note:** `CreateSubaccount` must be called using an API key from the master account.\\n\\n**API Key Permissions Required:** `Funds permissions - Withdraw`\\n\",\"deprecated\":null,\"version\":null,\"openapi\":\"/openapi/spot-rest.yaml post /private/CreateSubaccount\",\"href\":\"/api-reference/subaccounts/create-subaccount\",\"autogeneratedByOpenApi\":true},{\"title\":\"Account Transfer\",\"description\":\"Transfer funds to and from master and subaccounts. **Note:** `AccountTransfer` must be called using an API key from the master account.\\n\\n**API Key Permissions Required:** `Funds permissions - Withdraw`\\n\",\"deprecated\":null,\"version\":null,\"openapi\":\"/openapi/spot-rest.yaml post /private/AccountTransfer\",\"href\":\"/api-reference/subaccounts/account-transfer\",\"autogeneratedByOpenApi\":true}]},{\"group\":\"Earn\",\"public\":true,\"pages\":[{\"title\":\"List Earn Strategies\",\"description\":\"List earn strategies along with their parameters.\\n\\nRequires a valid API key but not specific permission is required.\\n\\nReturns only strategies that are available to the user\\nbased on geographic region.\\n\\nWhen the user does not meet the tier restriction, `can_allocate` will be\\nfalse and `allocation_restriction_info` indicates `Tier` as the restriction\\nreason. Earn products generally require Intermediate tier. Get your account verified\\nto access earn.\\n\\nA note about `lock_type`:\\n- `instant`: can be deallocated without an unbonding period. This is called flexible in the UI.\\n- `bonded`: has an unbonding period. Deallocation will not happen until this period has passed.\\n- `flex`: \\\"Kraken rewards\\\". This is earning on your spot balances where eligible. It's turned on account wide\\n  from the UI and you cannot manually allocate to these strategies.\\n\\nPaging isn't yet implemented, so the endpoint always returns all\\ndata in the first page.\",\"deprecated\":null,\"version\":null,\"openapi\":\"/openapi/spot-rest.yaml post /private/Earn/Strategies\",\"href\":\"/api-reference/earn/list-earn-strategies\",\"autogeneratedByOpenApi\":true},{\"title\":\"List Earn Allocations\",\"description\":\"$36\",\"deprecated\":null,\"version\":null,\"openapi\":\"/openapi/spot-rest.yaml post /private/Earn/Allocations\",\"href\":\"/api-reference/earn/list-earn-allocations\",\"autogeneratedByOpenApi\":true},{\"title\":\"Allocate Earn Funds\",\"description\":\"$37\",\"deprecated\":null,\"version\":null,\"openapi\":\"/openapi/spot-rest.yaml post /private/Earn/Allocate\",\"href\":\"/api-reference/earn/allocate-earn-funds\",\"autogeneratedByOpenApi\":true},{\"title\":\"Deallocate Earn Funds\",\"description\":\"$38\",\"deprecated\":null,\"version\":null,\"openapi\":\"/openapi/spot-rest.yaml post /private/Earn/Deallocate\",\"href\":\"/api-reference/earn/deallocate-earn-funds\",\"autogeneratedByOpenApi\":true},{\"title\":\"Get Allocation Status\",\"description\":\"$39\",\"deprecated\":null,\"version\":null,\"openapi\":\"/openapi/spot-rest.yaml post /private/Earn/AllocateStatus\",\"href\":\"/api-reference/earn/get-allocation-status\",\"autogeneratedByOpenApi\":true},{\"title\":\"Get Deallocation Status\",\"description\":\"Get the status of the last deallocation request.\\n\\nRequires either the `Earn Funds` or `Query Funds` API key permission.\\n\\n(De)allocation operations are asynchronous and this endpoint allows client\\nto retrieve the status of the last dispatched operation. There can be only\\none (de)allocation request in progress for given user and strategy.\\n\\nThe `pending` attribute in the response indicates if the previously\\ndispatched operation is still in progress (true) or has successfully\\ncompleted (false).  If the dispatched request failed with an error, then\\nHTTP error is returned to the client as if it belonged to the original\\nrequest.\\n\\nFollowing specific errors within `Earnings` class can be returned by this\\nmethod:\\n- Insufficient funds: `EEarnings:Insufficient funds:Insufficient funds to complete the (de)allocation request`\\n- Minimum allocation: `EEarnings:Below min:(De)allocation operation amount less than minimum`\",\"deprecated\":null,\"version\":null,\"openapi\":\"/openapi/spot-rest.yaml post /private/Earn/DeallocateStatus\",\"href\":\"/api-reference/earn/get-deallocation-status\",\"autogeneratedByOpenApi\":true}]},{\"group\":\"Transparency\",\"public\":true,\"pages\":[{\"title\":\"Pre-Trade Data\",\"description\":\"Returns the price levels in the order book with aggregated order quantities at each price level. \\nThe top 10 levels are returned for each trading pair.\\n\",\"deprecated\":null,\"version\":null,\"openapi\":\"/openapi/spot-rest.yaml get /public/PreTrade\",\"href\":\"/api-reference/transparency/pre-trade-data\",\"autogeneratedByOpenApi\":true},{\"title\":\"Post-Trade Data\",\"description\":\"Returns a list of trades on the spot exchange. \\nIf no filter parameters are specified, the last 1000 trades for all pairs are received.\\n\",\"deprecated\":null,\"version\":null,\"openapi\":\"/openapi/spot-rest.yaml get /public/PostTrade\",\"href\":\"/api-reference/transparency/post-trade-data\",\"autogeneratedByOpenApi\":true}]}]},{\"dropdown\":\"Spot WebSocket v2\",\"icon\":\"bolt\",\"pages\":[{\"title\":\"Spot WebSocket\",\"sidebarTitle\":\"Spot WebSocket\",\"description\":\"Reference for the Spot WebSocket API — v2 (recommended) and v1 (maintained)\",\"public\":true,\"href\":\"/exchange/api-reference/spot-websocket\"},{\"group\":\"Public Channels\",\"public\":true,\"pages\":[{\"title\":\"Ticker\",\"tag\":\"WSS\",\"description\":\"Subscribe to level 1 market data (top of book and recent trades)\",\"href\":\"/exchange/api-reference/spot-websocket-v2/ticker\"},{\"title\":\"Book (Level 2)\",\"tag\":\"WSS\",\"description\":\"Subscribe to level 2 order book data with aggregated quantities at each price level\",\"href\":\"/exchange/api-reference/spot-websocket-v2/book\"},{\"title\":\"Candles (OHLC)\",\"tag\":\"WSS\",\"description\":\"Subscribe to Open, High, Low and Close (OHLC) candle data for specific interval periods\",\"href\":\"/exchange/api-reference/spot-websocket-v2/ohlc\"},{\"title\":\"Trades\",\"tag\":\"WSS\",\"description\":\"Subscribe to real-time trade events when orders are matched in the book\",\"href\":\"/exchange/api-reference/spot-websocket-v2/trade\"},{\"title\":\"Instruments\",\"tag\":\"WSS\",\"description\":\"Subscribe to reference data for all active assets and tradeable pairs\",\"href\":\"/exchange/api-reference/spot-websocket-v2/instrument\"},{\"title\":\"Orders (Level 3)\",\"tag\":\"WSS\",\"description\":\"Subscribe to individual order visibility in the order book\",\"href\":\"/exchange/api-reference/spot-websocket-v2/level3\"},{\"title\":\"Status\",\"tag\":\"WSS\",\"description\":\"Receive exchange status updates and connection verification\",\"href\":\"/exchange/api-reference/spot-websocket-v2/status\"},{\"title\":\"Heartbeat\",\"tag\":\"WSS\",\"description\":\"Automatic heartbeat messages to verify the connection is alive\",\"href\":\"/exchange/api-reference/spot-websocket-v2/heartbeat\"}]},{\"group\":\"Trading\",\"public\":true,\"pages\":[{\"title\":\"Add Order\",\"tag\":\"WSS\",\"description\":\"Send a new order into the exchange via WebSocket\",\"href\":\"/exchange/api-reference/spot-websocket-v2/add_order\"},{\"title\":\"Edit Order\",\"tag\":\"WSS\",\"description\":\"Edit the parameters of a live order\",\"href\":\"/exchange/api-reference/spot-websocket-v2/edit_order\"},{\"title\":\"Amend Order\",\"tag\":\"WSS\",\"description\":\"Amend the parameters of a live order in-place\",\"href\":\"/exchange/api-reference/spot-websocket-v2/amend_order\"},{\"title\":\"Cancel Order\",\"tag\":\"WSS\",\"description\":\"Cancel one or more open orders via WebSocket\",\"href\":\"/exchange/api-reference/spot-websocket-v2/cancel_order\"},{\"title\":\"Cancel All\",\"tag\":\"WSS\",\"description\":\"Cancel all open orders\",\"href\":\"/exchange/api-reference/spot-websocket-v2/cancel_all\"},{\"title\":\"Cancel on Disconnect\",\"tag\":\"WSS\",\"description\":\"Dead Man's Switch mechanism to cancel all orders after a timeout\",\"href\":\"/exchange/api-reference/spot-websocket-v2/cancel_after\"},{\"title\":\"Batch Add\",\"tag\":\"WSS\",\"description\":\"Submit a batch of orders in a single request\",\"href\":\"/exchange/api-reference/spot-websocket-v2/batch_add\"},{\"title\":\"Batch Cancel\",\"tag\":\"WSS\",\"description\":\"Cancel multiple orders in a single request\",\"href\":\"/exchange/api-reference/spot-websocket-v2/batch_cancel\"}]},{\"group\":\"Account\",\"public\":true,\"pages\":[{\"title\":\"Balances\",\"tag\":\"WSS\",\"description\":\"Subscribe to client asset balances and account ledger transactions\",\"href\":\"/exchange/api-reference/spot-websocket-v2/balances\"},{\"title\":\"Executions\",\"tag\":\"WSS\",\"description\":\"Subscribe to order status and execution events for your account\",\"href\":\"/exchange/api-reference/spot-websocket-v2/executions\"}]},{\"group\":\"System\",\"public\":true,\"pages\":[{\"title\":\"Ping\",\"tag\":\"WSS\",\"description\":\"Verify the WebSocket connection is alive with a ping/pong request\",\"href\":\"/exchange/api-reference/spot-websocket-v2/ping\"}]}]},{\"dropdown\":\"Unified WebSocket\",\"icon\":\"lock\",\"hidden\":true,\"groups\":[{\"group\":\"Public Channels\",\"public\":true,\"pages\":[{\"title\":\"Ticker\",\"tag\":\"UWS\",\"description\":\"Subscribe to level 1 market data (top of book and recent trades)\",\"href\":\"/exchange/api-reference/unified-ws/ticker\"},{\"title\":\"Book (Level 2)\",\"tag\":\"UWS\",\"description\":\"Subscribe to level 2 order book data with aggregated quantities at each price level\",\"href\":\"/exchange/api-reference/unified-ws/book\"},{\"title\":\"Candles (OHLC)\",\"tag\":\"UWS\",\"description\":\"Subscribe to Open, High, Low and Close (OHLC) candle data for specific interval periods\",\"href\":\"/exchange/api-reference/unified-ws/ohlc\"},{\"title\":\"Instruments\",\"tag\":\"UWS\",\"description\":\"Subscribe to reference data for all active assets and tradeable pairs\",\"href\":\"/exchange/api-reference/unified-ws/instrument\"},{\"title\":\"Orders (Level 3)\",\"tag\":\"UWS\",\"description\":\"Subscribe to individual order visibility in the order book\",\"href\":\"/exchange/api-reference/unified-ws/level3\"},{\"title\":\"Status\",\"tag\":\"UWS\",\"description\":\"Receive exchange status updates and connection verification\",\"href\":\"/exchange/api-reference/unified-ws/status\"},{\"title\":\"Heartbeat\",\"tag\":\"UWS\",\"description\":\"Automatic heartbeat messages to verify the connection is alive\",\"href\":\"/exchange/api-reference/unified-ws/heartbeat\"}]},{\"group\":\"Trading\",\"public\":true,\"pages\":[{\"title\":\"Add Order\",\"tag\":\"UWS\",\"description\":\"Send a new order into the exchange via WebSocket\",\"href\":\"/exchange/api-reference/unified-ws/add_order\"},{\"title\":\"Amend Order\",\"tag\":\"UWS\",\"description\":\"Amend the parameters of a live order in-place\",\"href\":\"/exchange/api-reference/unified-ws/amend_order\"},{\"title\":\"Cancel Order\",\"tag\":\"UWS\",\"description\":\"Cancel one or more open orders via WebSocket\",\"href\":\"/exchange/api-reference/unified-ws/cancel_order\"},{\"title\":\"Cancel All\",\"tag\":\"UWS\",\"description\":\"Cancel all open orders\",\"href\":\"/exchange/api-reference/unified-ws/cancel_all\"},{\"title\":\"Cancel on Disconnect\",\"tag\":\"UWS\",\"description\":\"Dead Man's Switch mechanism to cancel all orders after a timeout\",\"href\":\"/exchange/api-reference/unified-ws/cancel_after\"}]},{\"group\":\"Account\",\"public\":true,\"pages\":[{\"title\":\"Balances\",\"tag\":\"UWS\",\"description\":\"Subscribe to client asset balances and account ledger transactions\",\"href\":\"/exchange/api-reference/unified-ws/balances\"},{\"title\":\"Executions\",\"tag\":\"UWS\",\"description\":\"Subscribe to order status and execution events for your account\",\"href\":\"/exchange/api-reference/unified-ws/executions\"}]},{\"group\":\"System\",\"public\":true,\"pages\":[{\"title\":\"Ping\",\"tag\":\"UWS\",\"description\":\"Verify the WebSocket connection is alive with a ping/pong request\",\"href\":\"/exchange/api-reference/unified-ws/ping\"}]}]},{\"dropdown\":\"Spot WebSocket v1\",\"icon\":\"bolt\",\"groups\":[{\"group\":\"Public Channels\",\"public\":true,\"pages\":[{\"title\":\"Ticker\",\"tag\":\"WSS\",\"description\":\"Subscribe to ticker information on currency pairs\",\"href\":\"/exchange/api-reference/spot-websocket-v1/ticker\"},{\"title\":\"Candles (OHLC)\",\"tag\":\"WSS\",\"description\":\"Subscribe to Open High Low Close candle feed for currency pairs\",\"href\":\"/exchange/api-reference/spot-websocket-v1/ohlc\"},{\"title\":\"Trade\",\"tag\":\"WSS\",\"description\":\"Subscribe to trade feed for currency pairs\",\"href\":\"/exchange/api-reference/spot-websocket-v1/trade\"},{\"title\":\"Spread\",\"tag\":\"WSS\",\"description\":\"Subscribe to spread feed for currency pairs\",\"href\":\"/exchange/api-reference/spot-websocket-v1/spread\"},{\"title\":\"Book\",\"tag\":\"WSS\",\"description\":\"Subscribe to order book levels (Level 2)\",\"href\":\"/exchange/api-reference/spot-websocket-v1/book\"}]},{\"group\":\"Trading\",\"public\":true,\"pages\":[{\"title\":\"Add Order\",\"tag\":\"WSS\",\"description\":\"Send a single new order into the exchange\",\"href\":\"/exchange/api-reference/spot-websocket-v1/addorder\"},{\"title\":\"Edit Order\",\"tag\":\"WSS\",\"description\":\"Edit the parameters of a live order by cancelling and recreating it\",\"href\":\"/exchange/api-reference/spot-websocket-v1/editorder\"},{\"title\":\"Amend Order\",\"tag\":\"WSS\",\"description\":\"Modify order parameters in-place without cancelling and recreating\",\"href\":\"/exchange/api-reference/spot-websocket-v1/amendorder\"},{\"title\":\"Cancel Order\",\"tag\":\"WSS\",\"description\":\"Cancel one or more open orders\",\"href\":\"/exchange/api-reference/spot-websocket-v1/cancelorder\"},{\"title\":\"Cancel All\",\"tag\":\"WSS\",\"description\":\"Cancel all open orders including partially-filled orders\",\"href\":\"/exchange/api-reference/spot-websocket-v1/cancelall\"},{\"title\":\"Cancel on Disconnect\",\"tag\":\"WSS\",\"description\":\"Dead Man's Switch mechanism to cancel all orders after a timeout\",\"href\":\"/exchange/api-reference/spot-websocket-v1/cancelallordersafter\"}]},{\"group\":\"Account\",\"public\":true,\"pages\":[{\"title\":\"Own Trades\",\"tag\":\"WSS\",\"description\":\"Subscribe to real-time trade execution updates for the authenticated user\",\"href\":\"/exchange/api-reference/spot-websocket-v1/owntrades\"},{\"title\":\"Open Orders\",\"tag\":\"WSS\",\"description\":\"Subscribe to real-time open order updates for the authenticated user\",\"href\":\"/exchange/api-reference/spot-websocket-v1/openorders\"}]},{\"group\":\"System\",\"public\":true,\"pages\":[{\"title\":\"Ping\",\"tag\":\"WSS\",\"description\":\"Client ping to determine whether the connection is alive\",\"href\":\"/exchange/api-reference/spot-websocket-v1/ping\"},{\"title\":\"Heartbeat\",\"tag\":\"WSS\",\"description\":\"Server heartbeat sent when no subscription traffic is detected\",\"href\":\"/exchange/api-reference/spot-websocket-v1/heartbeat\"},{\"title\":\"System Status\",\"tag\":\"WSS\",\"description\":\"Server-pushed system status on connection or status changes\",\"href\":\"/exchange/api-reference/spot-websocket-v1/systemstatus\"},{\"title\":\"Subscription Status\",\"tag\":\"WSS\",\"description\":\"Server-pushed subscription status response to subscribe, unsubscribe, or exchange-initiated unsubscribe\",\"href\":\"/exchange/api-reference/spot-websocket-v1/subscriptionstatus\"},{\"title\":\"Unsubscribe\",\"tag\":\"WSS\",\"description\":\"Unsubscribe from one or more WebSocket channels\",\"href\":\"/exchange/api-reference/spot-websocket-v1/unsubscribe\"}]}]},{\"dropdown\":\"Derivatives REST\",\"icon\":\"code\",\"groups\":[{\"group\":\"Market Data\",\"public\":true,\"pages\":[{\"title\":\"Get tickers\",\"description\":\"This endpoint returns current market data for all currently listed Futures contracts and\\nindices.\",\"deprecated\":null,\"version\":null,\"openapi\":\"/openapi/futures-rest.yaml get /tickers\",\"href\":\"/api-reference/market-data/get-tickers\",\"autogeneratedByOpenApi\":true},{\"title\":\"Get ticker by symbol\",\"description\":\"Get market data for contract or index by symbol\",\"deprecated\":null,\"version\":null,\"openapi\":\"/openapi/futures-rest.yaml get /tickers/{symbol}\",\"href\":\"/api-reference/market-data/get-ticker-by-symbol\",\"autogeneratedByOpenApi\":true},{\"title\":\"Get orderbook\",\"description\":\"This endpoint returns the entire non-cumulative order book of currently listed Futures\\ncontracts.\",\"deprecated\":null,\"version\":null,\"openapi\":\"/openapi/futures-rest.yaml get /orderbook\",\"href\":\"/api-reference/market-data/get-orderbook\",\"autogeneratedByOpenApi\":true},{\"title\":\"Get trade history\",\"description\":\"This endpoint returns the most recent 100 trades prior to the specified `lastTime` value up\\nto past 7 days or recent trading engine restart (whichever is sooner).\\n\\nIf no `lastTime` specified, it will return 100 most recent trades.\",\"deprecated\":null,\"version\":null,\"openapi\":\"/openapi/futures-rest.yaml get /history\",\"href\":\"/api-reference/market-data/get-trade-history\",\"autogeneratedByOpenApi\":true}]},{\"group\":\"Instruments\",\"public\":true,\"pages\":[{\"title\":\"Get instruments\",\"description\":\"Returns specifications for all currently listed markets and indices.\",\"deprecated\":null,\"version\":null,\"openapi\":\"/openapi/futures-rest.yaml get /instruments\",\"href\":\"/api-reference/instrument-details/get-instruments\",\"autogeneratedByOpenApi\":true},{\"title\":\"Get trading instruments\",\"description\":\"Returns specifications for all currently accessible markets and indices.\",\"deprecated\":null,\"version\":null,\"openapi\":\"/openapi/futures-rest.yaml get /trading/instruments\",\"href\":\"/api-reference/instrument-details/get-trading-instruments\",\"autogeneratedByOpenApi\":true},{\"title\":\"Get instrument status list\",\"description\":\"Returns price dislocation and volatility details for all markets.\",\"deprecated\":null,\"version\":null,\"openapi\":\"/openapi/futures-rest.yaml get /instruments/status\",\"href\":\"/api-reference/instrument-details/get-instrument-status-list\",\"autogeneratedByOpenApi\":true},{\"title\":\"Get instrument status\",\"description\":\"Returns price dislocation and volatility details for given market.\",\"deprecated\":null,\"version\":null,\"openapi\":\"/openapi/futures-rest.yaml get /instruments/{symbol}/status\",\"href\":\"/api-reference/instrument-details/get-instrument-status\",\"autogeneratedByOpenApi\":true}]},{\"group\":\"Order Management\",\"public\":true,\"pages\":[{\"title\":\"Send order\",\"description\":\"This endpoint allows sending a limit, stop, take profit or immediate-or-cancel order for a\\ncurrently listed Futures contract.\",\"deprecated\":null,\"version\":null,\"openapi\":\"/openapi/futures-rest.yaml post /sendorder\",\"href\":\"/api-reference/order-management/send-order\",\"autogeneratedByOpenApi\":true},{\"title\":\"Edit order\",\"description\":\"This endpoint allows editing an existing order for a currently listed Futures contract.\\n\\nWhen editing an order, if the `trailingStopMaxDeviation` and `trailingStopDeviationUnit`\\nparameters are sent unchanged, the system will recalculate a new stop price upon successful\\norder modification.\",\"deprecated\":null,\"version\":null,\"openapi\":\"/openapi/futures-rest.yaml post /editorder\",\"href\":\"/api-reference/order-management/edit-order\",\"autogeneratedByOpenApi\":true},{\"title\":\"Cancel order\",\"description\":\"This endpoint allows cancelling an open order for a Futures contract.\",\"deprecated\":null,\"version\":null,\"openapi\":\"/openapi/futures-rest.yaml post /cancelorder\",\"href\":\"/api-reference/order-management/cancel-order\",\"autogeneratedByOpenApi\":true},{\"title\":\"Cancel all orders\",\"description\":\"This endpoint allows cancelling orders which are associated with a future's contract or a\\nmargin account. If no arguments are specified all open orders will be cancelled.\",\"deprecated\":null,\"version\":null,\"openapi\":\"/openapi/futures-rest.yaml post /cancelallorders\",\"href\":\"/api-reference/order-management/cancel-all-orders\",\"autogeneratedByOpenApi\":true},{\"title\":\"Dead man's switch\",\"description\":\"This endpoint provides a Dead Man's Switch mechanism to protect the user from network malfunctions. The user can send a request with a timeout in seconds which will trigger a countdown timer that will cancel all user orders when timeout expires. The user has to keep sending request to push back the timeout expiration or they can deactivate the mechanism by specifying a timeout of zero (0).\\n\\nThe recommended mechanism usage is making a call every 15 to 20 seconds and provide a timeout of 60 seconds. This allows the user to keep the orders in place on a brief network failure, while keeping them safe in case of a network breakdown.\",\"deprecated\":null,\"version\":null,\"openapi\":\"/openapi/futures-rest.yaml post /cancelallordersafter\",\"href\":\"/api-reference/order-management/dead-mans-switch\",\"autogeneratedByOpenApi\":true},{\"title\":\"Batch order management\",\"description\":\"This endpoint allows sending limit or stop order(s) and/or cancelling open order(s) and/or\\nediting open order(s) for a currently listed Futures contract in batch.\\n\\nWhen editing an order, if the `trailingStopMaxDeviation` and `trailingStopDeviationUnit`\\nparameters are sent unchanged, the system will recalculate a new stop price upon successful\\norder modification.\",\"deprecated\":null,\"version\":null,\"openapi\":\"/openapi/futures-rest.yaml post /batchorder\",\"href\":\"/api-reference/order-management/batch-order-management\",\"autogeneratedByOpenApi\":true},{\"title\":\"Get open orders\",\"description\":\"This endpoint returns information on all open orders for all Futures contracts.\",\"deprecated\":null,\"version\":null,\"openapi\":\"/openapi/futures-rest.yaml get /openorders\",\"href\":\"/api-reference/order-management/get-open-orders\",\"autogeneratedByOpenApi\":true},{\"title\":\"Get Specific Orders' Status\",\"description\":\"Returns information on specified orders which are open or were filled/cancelled in the last\\n5 seconds.\",\"deprecated\":null,\"version\":null,\"openapi\":\"/openapi/futures-rest.yaml post /orders/status\",\"href\":\"/api-reference/order-management/get-specific-orders-status\",\"autogeneratedByOpenApi\":true}]},{\"group\":\"Account\",\"public\":true,\"pages\":[{\"title\":\"Get wallets\",\"description\":\"This endpoint returns key information relating to all your accounts which may either be\\ncash accounts or margin accounts. This includes digital asset balances, instrument balances,\\nmargin requirements, margin trigger estimates and auxiliary information such as available\\nfunds, PnL of open positions and portfolio value.\",\"deprecated\":null,\"version\":null,\"openapi\":\"/openapi/futures-rest.yaml get /accounts\",\"href\":\"/api-reference/account-information/get-wallets\",\"autogeneratedByOpenApi\":true},{\"title\":\"Get open positions\",\"description\":\"This endpoint returns the size and average entry price of all open positions in Futures\\ncontracts. This includes Futures contracts that have matured but have not yet been settled.\",\"deprecated\":null,\"version\":null,\"openapi\":\"/openapi/futures-rest.yaml get /openpositions\",\"href\":\"/api-reference/account-information/get-open-positions\",\"autogeneratedByOpenApi\":true},{\"title\":\"Get position percentile of unwind queue\",\"description\":\"This endpoint returns the percentile of the open position in case of unwinding.\",\"deprecated\":null,\"version\":null,\"openapi\":\"/openapi/futures-rest.yaml get /unwindqueue\",\"href\":\"/api-reference/account-information/get-position-percentile-of-unwind-queue\",\"autogeneratedByOpenApi\":true},{\"title\":\"Get portfolio margin parameters\",\"description\":\"Retrieve current portfolio margin calculation parameters.\\n\\nAlso includes user specific limits related to options trading.\\n\\nNote: This is currently available exclusively in the Kraken pre-prod environments.\",\"deprecated\":null,\"version\":null,\"openapi\":\"/openapi/futures-rest.yaml get /portfolio-margining/parameters\",\"href\":\"/api-reference/account-information/get-portfolio-margin-parameters\",\"autogeneratedByOpenApi\":true},{\"title\":\"Calculate portfolio margin, pnl and greeks\",\"description\":\"For a given portfolio of balances and positions (futures and options), calculate the\\nmargin requirements, pnl and option greeks.\\n\\nNote: This is currently available exclusively in the Kraken pre-prod environments.\",\"deprecated\":null,\"version\":null,\"openapi\":\"/openapi/futures-rest.yaml post /portfolio-margining/simulate\",\"href\":\"/api-reference/account-information/calculate-portfolio-margin-pnl-and-greeks\",\"autogeneratedByOpenApi\":true}]},{\"group\":\"Multi-Collateral\",\"public\":true,\"pages\":[{\"title\":\"Get PNL currency preferences\",\"description\":\"The PNL currency preference is used to determine which currency to pay out when realizing\\nPNL gains.\",\"deprecated\":null,\"version\":null,\"openapi\":\"/openapi/futures-rest.yaml get /pnlpreferences\",\"href\":\"/api-reference/multi-collateral/get-pnl-currency-preferences\",\"autogeneratedByOpenApi\":true},{\"title\":\"Set PNL currency preference\",\"description\":\"The PNL currency preference is used to determine which currency to pay out when realizing\\nPNL gains. Calling this API can result in the following error codes:\\n\\n\\n  87: Contract does not exist\\n\\n  88: Contract not a multi-collateral futures contract\\n\\n  89: Currency does not exist\\n\\n  90: Currency is not enabled for multi-collateral futures\\n\\n  41: Would cause liquidation\",\"deprecated\":null,\"version\":null,\"openapi\":\"/openapi/futures-rest.yaml put /pnlpreferences\",\"href\":\"/api-reference/multi-collateral/set-pnl-currency-preference\",\"autogeneratedByOpenApi\":true},{\"title\":\"Get leverage settings\",\"description\":\"Returns list of configured leverage preferences.\",\"deprecated\":null,\"version\":null,\"openapi\":\"/openapi/futures-rest.yaml get /leveragepreferences\",\"href\":\"/api-reference/multi-collateral/get-leverage-settings\",\"autogeneratedByOpenApi\":true},{\"title\":\"Set leverage settings\",\"description\":\"Sets a contract's margin mode, either \\\"isolated\\\" or \\\"cross\\\" margin.\\n\\nWhen specifying a max leverage, the contract's margin mode will be isolated.\\n\\nCalling this endpoint can result in the following error codes:\\n- 87: Contract does not exist\\n- 88: Contract not a multi-collateral futures contract\\n- 41: Would cause liquidation\",\"deprecated\":null,\"version\":null,\"openapi\":\"/openapi/futures-rest.yaml put /leveragepreferences\",\"href\":\"/api-reference/multi-collateral/set-leverage-settings\",\"autogeneratedByOpenApi\":true}]},{\"group\":\"Fee Schedules\",\"public\":true,\"pages\":[{\"title\":\"Get fee schedules\",\"description\":\"**DEPRECATED** — Effective 2026-06-22, the fee values returned by this\\nendpoint no longer reflect the fees actually charged on Futures trades.\\nFutures fee calculation has been migrated to a centralised Kraken fee\\nservice.\\n\\nTo determine the fee rate applied to your trades, use the Spot\\n[`GetTradeVolume`](https://docs.kraken.com/api/docs/rest-api/get-trade-volume)\\nendpoint authenticated with a Spot API key.\\n\\n---\\n\\nThis endpoint lists all fee schedules.\",\"deprecated\":true,\"version\":null,\"openapi\":\"/openapi/futures-rest.yaml get /feeschedules\",\"href\":\"/api-reference/fee-schedules/get-fee-schedules\",\"autogeneratedByOpenApi\":true},{\"title\":\"Get fee schedule volumes\",\"description\":\"**DEPRECATED** — Effective 2026-06-22, the volumes and fee schedule\\nassociations returned by this endpoint no longer reflect the fees\\nactually charged on Futures trades. Futures fee calculation has been\\nmigrated to a centralised Kraken fee service.\\n\\nTo determine the fee rate applied to your trades, use the Spot\\n[`GetTradeVolume`](https://docs.kraken.com/api/docs/rest-api/get-trade-volume)\\nendpoint authenticated with a Spot API key.\\n\\n---\\n\\nReturns your fee schedule volumes for each fee schedule.\",\"deprecated\":true,\"version\":null,\"openapi\":\"/openapi/futures-rest.yaml get /feeschedules/volumes\",\"href\":\"/api-reference/fee-schedules/get-fee-schedule-volumes\",\"autogeneratedByOpenApi\":true}]},{\"group\":\"Historical Data\",\"public\":true,\"pages\":[{\"title\":\"Get your fills\",\"description\":\"This endpoint returns information on your filled orders for all futures contracts.\",\"deprecated\":null,\"version\":null,\"openapi\":\"/openapi/futures-rest.yaml get /fills\",\"href\":\"/api-reference/historical-data/get-your-fills\",\"autogeneratedByOpenApi\":true},{\"title\":\"Historical funding rates\",\"description\":\"Returns list of historical funding rates for given market.\",\"deprecated\":null,\"version\":null,\"openapi\":\"/openapi/futures-rest.yaml get /historical-funding-rates\",\"href\":\"/api-reference/historical-funding-rates/historical-funding-rates\",\"autogeneratedByOpenApi\":true}]},{\"group\":\"Trading Settings\",\"public\":true,\"pages\":[{\"title\":\"Get self trade strategy\",\"description\":\"Returns account-wide self-trade matching strategy.\",\"deprecated\":null,\"version\":null,\"openapi\":\"/openapi/futures-rest.yaml get /self-trade-strategy\",\"href\":\"/api-reference/trading-settings/get-self-trade-strategy\",\"autogeneratedByOpenApi\":true},{\"title\":\"Update self trade strategy\",\"description\":\"Updates account-wide self-trade matching behavior to given strategy.\",\"deprecated\":null,\"version\":null,\"openapi\":\"/openapi/futures-rest.yaml put /self-trade-strategy\",\"href\":\"/api-reference/trading-settings/update-self-trade-strategy\",\"autogeneratedByOpenApi\":true}]},{\"group\":\"Subaccounts\",\"public\":true,\"pages\":[{\"title\":\"Get subaccounts\",\"description\":\"Return information about subaccounts, including balances and UIDs.\",\"deprecated\":null,\"version\":null,\"openapi\":\"/openapi/futures-rest.yaml get /subaccounts\",\"href\":\"/api-reference/subaccounts/get-subaccounts\",\"autogeneratedByOpenApi\":true},{\"title\":\"Check subaccount trading status\",\"description\":\"Returns trading capability info for given subaccount.\",\"deprecated\":null,\"version\":null,\"openapi\":\"/openapi/futures-rest.yaml get /subaccount/{subaccountUid}/trading-enabled\",\"href\":\"/api-reference/subaccounts/check-subaccount-trading-status\",\"autogeneratedByOpenApi\":true},{\"title\":\"Update subaccount trading status\",\"description\":\"Updates trading capabilities for given subaccount.\",\"deprecated\":null,\"version\":null,\"openapi\":\"/openapi/futures-rest.yaml put /subaccount/{subaccountUid}/trading-enabled\",\"href\":\"/api-reference/subaccounts/update-subaccount-trading-status\",\"autogeneratedByOpenApi\":true}]},{\"group\":\"Transfers\",\"public\":true,\"pages\":[{\"title\":\"Initiate wallet transfer\",\"description\":\"This endpoint allows you to transfer funds between two margin accounts with the same\\ncollateral currency, or between a margin account and your cash account.\",\"deprecated\":null,\"version\":null,\"openapi\":\"/openapi/futures-rest.yaml post /transfer\",\"href\":\"/api-reference/transfers/initiate-wallet-transfer\",\"autogeneratedByOpenApi\":true},{\"title\":\"Initiate sub account transfer\",\"description\":\"This endpoint allows you to transfer funds between the current account and a sub account,\\nbetween two margin accounts with the same collateral currency, or between a margin account\\nand your cash account.\",\"deprecated\":null,\"version\":null,\"openapi\":\"/openapi/futures-rest.yaml post /transfer/subaccount\",\"href\":\"/api-reference/transfers/initiate-sub-account-transfer\",\"autogeneratedByOpenApi\":true},{\"title\":\"Initiate withdrawal to Spot wallet\",\"description\":\"This endpoint allows you to request to withdraw digital assets to your Kraken Spot wallet.\\n\\nWallet names can be found in the 'accounts' structure in the Get Wallets /accounts response.\",\"deprecated\":null,\"version\":null,\"openapi\":\"/openapi/futures-rest.yaml post /withdrawal\",\"href\":\"/api-reference/transfers/initiate-withdrawal-to-spot-wallet\",\"autogeneratedByOpenApi\":true}]},{\"group\":\"Assignment Program\",\"public\":true,\"pages\":[{\"title\":\"List assignment programs\",\"description\":\"This endpoint returns information on currently active assignment programs\",\"deprecated\":null,\"version\":null,\"openapi\":\"/openapi/futures-rest.yaml get /assignmentprogram/current\",\"href\":\"/api-reference/assignment-program/list-assignment-programs\",\"autogeneratedByOpenApi\":true},{\"title\":\"Add assignment preference\",\"description\":\"This endpoint adds an assignment program preference\",\"deprecated\":null,\"version\":null,\"openapi\":\"/openapi/futures-rest.yaml post /assignmentprogram/add\",\"href\":\"/api-reference/assignment-program/add-assignment-preference\",\"autogeneratedByOpenApi\":true},{\"title\":\"Deletes assignment preference\",\"description\":\"This endpoint deletes an assignment program preference\",\"deprecated\":null,\"version\":null,\"openapi\":\"/openapi/futures-rest.yaml post /assignmentprogram/delete\",\"href\":\"/api-reference/assignment-program/deletes-assignment-preference\",\"autogeneratedByOpenApi\":true},{\"title\":\"List assignment preferences history\",\"description\":\"This endpoint returns information on assignment program preferences change history\",\"deprecated\":null,\"version\":null,\"openapi\":\"/openapi/futures-rest.yaml get /assignmentprogram/history\",\"href\":\"/api-reference/assignment-program/list-assignment-preferences-history\",\"autogeneratedByOpenApi\":true}]},{\"group\":\"RFQs\",\"public\":true,\"pages\":[{\"title\":\"List all open RFQs\",\"description\":\"Retrieve all currently open RFQs\\n\\nNote: This is currently available exclusively in the Kraken pre-prod environments.\",\"deprecated\":null,\"version\":null,\"openapi\":\"/openapi/futures-rest.yaml get /rfqs\",\"href\":\"/api-reference/rfqs/list-all-open-rfqs\",\"autogeneratedByOpenApi\":true},{\"title\":\"Retrieve a single RFQ (open or recently closed)\",\"description\":\"Retrieve a specific RFQ by its unique identifier. Returns currently open RFQs as well as\\nrecently closed RFQs that are still held in the in-memory closed-RFQ cache. The `status`\\nfield on the response distinguishes the lifecycle state (`open`, `expired`, `cancelled`,\\n`filled_bid_side`, or `filled_ask_side`).\\n\\nClosed RFQs are kept in memory only and are not persisted; entries may be evicted by the\\ncache eviction policy or wiped on service restart.\\n\\nNote: This is currently available exclusively in the Kraken pre-prod environments.\",\"deprecated\":null,\"version\":null,\"openapi\":\"/openapi/futures-rest.yaml get /rfqs/{rfqUid}\",\"href\":\"/api-reference/rfqs/retrieve-a-single-rfq-open-or-recently-closed\",\"autogeneratedByOpenApi\":true},{\"title\":\"List open offers on open RFQs\",\"description\":\"Retrieve all open offers for the account on currently open RFQs\\n\\nNote: This is currently available exclusively in the Kraken pre-prod environments.\",\"deprecated\":null,\"version\":null,\"openapi\":\"/openapi/futures-rest.yaml get /rfqs/open-offers\",\"href\":\"/api-reference/rfqs/list-open-offers-on-open-rfqs\",\"autogeneratedByOpenApi\":true},{\"title\":\"List offers placed by the account on closed RFQs\",\"description\":\"Retrieve all offers the account placed on RFQs that have since closed. The `status` field\\non each offer indicates how the parent RFQ closed (`expired`, `cancelled`,\\n`filled_bid_side`, or `filled_ask_side`).\\n\\nClosed RFQs are tracked in an in-memory cache only and are not persisted; offers may be\\nevicted by the cache eviction policy or wiped on service restart.\\n\\nNote: This is currently available exclusively in the Kraken pre-prod environments.\",\"deprecated\":null,\"version\":null,\"openapi\":\"/openapi/futures-rest.yaml get /rfqs/closed-offers\",\"href\":\"/api-reference/rfqs/list-offers-placed-by-the-account-on-closed-rfqs\",\"autogeneratedByOpenApi\":true},{\"title\":\"Place new offer on an open RFQ\",\"description\":\"Place a new offer on the specified open RFQ. At least one of bid or ask must be provided.\\n\\nNote: This is currently available exclusively in the Kraken pre-prod environments.\",\"deprecated\":null,\"version\":null,\"openapi\":\"/openapi/futures-rest.yaml post /rfqs/place-offer/{rfqUid}\",\"href\":\"/api-reference/rfqs/place-new-offer-on-an-open-rfq\",\"autogeneratedByOpenApi\":true},{\"title\":\"Cancel open offer on open RFQ\",\"description\":\"Cancel the current open offer on the specified open RFQ.\\n\\nNote: This is currently available exclusively in the Kraken pre-prod environments.\",\"deprecated\":null,\"version\":null,\"openapi\":\"/openapi/futures-rest.yaml delete /rfqs/cancel-offer/{rfqUid}\",\"href\":\"/api-reference/rfqs/cancel-open-offer-on-open-rfq\",\"autogeneratedByOpenApi\":true},{\"title\":\"List open RFQs for account\",\"description\":\"Retrieve all currently open RFQs created by the authenticated account.\\n\\nNote: This is currently available exclusively in the Kraken pre-prod environments.\",\"deprecated\":null,\"version\":null,\"openapi\":\"/openapi/futures-rest.yaml get /rfqs/open-rfqs\",\"href\":\"/api-reference/rfqs/list-open-rfqs-for-account\",\"autogeneratedByOpenApi\":true},{\"title\":\"Create a new RFQ\",\"description\":\"Create a new RFQ for the authenticated account.\\n\\nNote: This is currently available exclusively in the Kraken pre-prod environments.\",\"deprecated\":null,\"version\":null,\"openapi\":\"/openapi/futures-rest.yaml post /rfqs/open-rfqs\",\"href\":\"/api-reference/rfqs/create-a-new-rfq\",\"autogeneratedByOpenApi\":true},{\"title\":\"Cancel an open RFQ\",\"description\":\"Cancel a specific open RFQ created by the authenticated account.\\n\\nNote: This is currently available exclusively in the Kraken pre-prod environments.\",\"deprecated\":null,\"version\":null,\"openapi\":\"/openapi/futures-rest.yaml delete /rfqs/open-rfqs/{rfqUid}\",\"href\":\"/api-reference/rfqs/cancel-an-open-rfq\",\"autogeneratedByOpenApi\":true},{\"title\":\"Accept an offer on an open RFQ\",\"description\":\"Accept an offer on a specific open RFQ created by the authenticated account.\\nExactly one of `bidAccepted` or `askAccepted` must be provided.\\n\\nNote: This is currently available exclusively in the Kraken pre-prod environments.\",\"deprecated\":null,\"version\":null,\"openapi\":\"/openapi/futures-rest.yaml post /rfqs/open-rfqs/accept-offer/{rfqUid}\",\"href\":\"/api-reference/rfqs/accept-an-offer-on-an-open-rfq\",\"autogeneratedByOpenApi\":true}]},{\"group\":\"General\",\"public\":true,\"pages\":[{\"title\":\"Get notifications\",\"description\":\"This endpoint provides the platform's notifications.\",\"deprecated\":null,\"version\":null,\"openapi\":\"/openapi/futures-rest.yaml get /notifications\",\"href\":\"/api-reference/general/get-notifications\",\"autogeneratedByOpenApi\":true}]},{\"group\":\"Account History\",\"public\":true,\"pages\":[{\"title\":\"Get execution events\",\"description\":\"Lists executions/trades for authenticated account.\\n\",\"deprecated\":null,\"version\":null,\"openapi\":\"/openapi/futures-history-rest.yaml get /executions\",\"href\":\"/api-reference/account-history/get-execution-events\",\"autogeneratedByOpenApi\":true},{\"title\":\"Get order events\",\"description\":\"Lists order events for authenticated account.\\n\",\"deprecated\":null,\"version\":null,\"openapi\":\"/openapi/futures-history-rest.yaml get /orders\",\"href\":\"/api-reference/account-history/get-order-events\",\"autogeneratedByOpenApi\":true},{\"title\":\"Get trigger events\",\"description\":\"Lists trigger events for authenticated account.\\n\",\"deprecated\":null,\"version\":null,\"openapi\":\"/openapi/futures-history-rest.yaml get /triggers\",\"href\":\"/api-reference/account-history/get-trigger-events\",\"autogeneratedByOpenApi\":true},{\"title\":\"Get position update events\",\"description\":\"Lists position events for authenticated account.\",\"deprecated\":null,\"version\":null,\"openapi\":\"/openapi/futures-history-rest.yaml get /positions\",\"href\":\"/api-reference/account-history/get-position-update-events\",\"autogeneratedByOpenApi\":true},{\"title\":\"Get account log\",\"description\":\"Lists account log entries, paged by timestamp or by ID.\\n\\nTo request entries by time range, use the `since` and `before` parameters.\\nTo request entries by ID range, use the `from` and `to` parameters.\\nAny combination of `since`, `before`, `from` and `to` can be used to restrict the requested range of entries.\\n\",\"deprecated\":null,\"version\":null,\"openapi\":\"/openapi/futures-history-rest.yaml get /account-log\",\"href\":\"/api-reference/account-history/get-account-log\",\"autogeneratedByOpenApi\":true},{\"title\":\"Account log (CSV)\",\"description\":\"Lists recent account log entries in CSV format.\\n\",\"deprecated\":null,\"version\":null,\"openapi\":\"/openapi/futures-history-rest.yaml get /accountlogcsv\",\"href\":\"/api-reference/account-history/account-log-csv\",\"autogeneratedByOpenApi\":true}]},{\"group\":\"Market History\",\"public\":true,\"pages\":[{\"title\":\"Get public execution events\",\"description\":\"Lists trades for a market.\\n\",\"deprecated\":null,\"version\":null,\"openapi\":\"/openapi/futures-history-rest.yaml get /market/{tradeable}/executions\",\"href\":\"/api-reference/market-history/get-public-execution-events\",\"autogeneratedByOpenApi\":true},{\"title\":\"Get public order events\",\"description\":\"Lists order events for a market.\\n\",\"deprecated\":null,\"version\":null,\"openapi\":\"/openapi/futures-history-rest.yaml get /market/{tradeable}/orders\",\"href\":\"/api-reference/market-history/get-public-order-events\",\"autogeneratedByOpenApi\":true},{\"title\":\"Get public mark price events\",\"description\":\"Lists price events for a market.\\n\",\"deprecated\":null,\"version\":null,\"openapi\":\"/openapi/futures-history-rest.yaml get /market/{tradeable}/price\",\"href\":\"/api-reference/market-history/get-public-mark-price-events\",\"autogeneratedByOpenApi\":true}]},{\"group\":\"Candles\",\"public\":true,\"pages\":[{\"title\":\"Tick Types\",\"description\":\"Returns all available tick types to use with the [markets](#operation/symbols) endpoint.\",\"deprecated\":null,\"version\":null,\"openapi\":\"/openapi/futures-charts-rest.yaml get /\",\"href\":\"/api-reference/candles/tick-types\",\"autogeneratedByOpenApi\":true},{\"title\":\"Markets\",\"description\":\"Markets available for specified tick type.\\n\\nList of available tick types can be fetched from the [tick types](#operation/tickTypes)\\nendpoint.\",\"deprecated\":null,\"version\":null,\"openapi\":\"/openapi/futures-charts-rest.yaml get /{tick_type}\",\"href\":\"/api-reference/candles/markets\",\"autogeneratedByOpenApi\":true},{\"title\":\"Resolutions\",\"description\":\"Candle resolutions available for specified tick type and market.\\n\\nList of available tick types can be fetched from the [tick types](#operation/tickTypes)\\nendpoint. List of available markets can be fetched from the [markets](#operation/symbols)\\nendpoint.\",\"deprecated\":null,\"version\":null,\"openapi\":\"/openapi/futures-charts-rest.yaml get /{tick_type}/{symbol}\",\"href\":\"/api-reference/candles/resolutions\",\"autogeneratedByOpenApi\":true},{\"title\":\"Market Candles\",\"description\":\"Candles for specified tick type, market, and resolution.\\n\\nList of available tick types can be fetched from the [tick types](#operation/tickTypes)\\nendpoint. List of available markets can be fetched from the [markets](#operation/symbols)\\nendpoint. List of available resolutions can be fetched from the\\n[resolutions](#operation/resolutions) endpoint.\",\"deprecated\":null,\"version\":null,\"openapi\":\"/openapi/futures-charts-rest.yaml get /{tick_type}/{symbol}/{resolution}\",\"href\":\"/api-reference/candles/market-candles\",\"autogeneratedByOpenApi\":true}]},{\"group\":\"Analytics\",\"public\":true,\"pages\":[{\"title\":\"Get liquidity pool statistic\",\"description\":\"Get liquidity pool statistic including usd value\",\"deprecated\":null,\"version\":null,\"openapi\":\"/openapi/futures-charts-rest.yaml get /analytics/liquidity-pool\",\"href\":\"/api-reference/analytics/get-liquidity-pool-statistic\",\"autogeneratedByOpenApi\":true},{\"title\":\"Market Analytics\",\"description\":\"Analytics data divided into time buckets\",\"deprecated\":null,\"version\":null,\"openapi\":\"/openapi/futures-charts-rest.yaml get /analytics/{symbol}/{analytics_type}\",\"href\":\"/api-reference/analytics/market-analytics\",\"autogeneratedByOpenApi\":true}]},{\"group\":\"API Keys\",\"public\":true,\"pages\":[{\"title\":\"Check v3 API key\",\"description\":\"Verify API key access and return the authenticated key's details.\",\"deprecated\":null,\"version\":null,\"openapi\":\"/openapi/futures-auth-rest.yaml get /api-keys/v3/check\",\"href\":\"/api-reference/api-keys/check-v3-api-key\",\"autogeneratedByOpenApi\":true}]}]},{\"dropdown\":\"Derivatives WebSocket\",\"icon\":\"bolt\",\"pages\":[{\"title\":\"Derivatives WebSocket\",\"sidebarTitle\":\"Derivatives WebSocket\",\"description\":\"Real-time market data and account streaming for the Kraken Derivatives WebSocket API\",\"public\":true,\"href\":\"/exchange/api-reference/futures-websocket\"},{\"group\":\"Public Channels\",\"public\":true,\"pages\":[{\"title\":\"Ticker\",\"tag\":\"WSS\",\"description\":\"Subscribe to ticker information about listed products\",\"href\":\"/exchange/api-reference/futures-websocket/ticker\"},{\"title\":\"Ticker Lite\",\"tag\":\"WSS\",\"description\":\"Subscribe to lightweight ticker information about listed products\",\"href\":\"/exchange/api-reference/futures-websocket/ticker_lite\"},{\"title\":\"Trade\",\"tag\":\"WSS\",\"description\":\"Subscribe to information about executed trades\",\"href\":\"/exchange/api-reference/futures-websocket/trade\"},{\"title\":\"Book\",\"tag\":\"WSS\",\"description\":\"Subscribe to order book data\",\"href\":\"/exchange/api-reference/futures-websocket/book\"},{\"title\":\"Heartbeat\",\"tag\":\"WSS\",\"description\":\"Subscribe to heartbeat messages at timed intervals\",\"href\":\"/exchange/api-reference/futures-websocket/heartbeat\"}]},{\"group\":\"Private Channels\",\"public\":true,\"pages\":[{\"title\":\"Balances\",\"tag\":\"WSS\",\"description\":\"Subscribe to balance information for holding, single collateral, and multi-collateral wallets\",\"href\":\"/exchange/api-reference/futures-websocket/balances\"},{\"title\":\"Fills\",\"tag\":\"WSS\",\"description\":\"Subscribe to fills information for your account\",\"href\":\"/exchange/api-reference/futures-websocket/fills\"},{\"title\":\"Open Orders\",\"tag\":\"WSS\",\"description\":\"Subscribe to open orders information for your account\",\"href\":\"/exchange/api-reference/futures-websocket/open_orders\"},{\"title\":\"Open Orders (Verbose)\",\"tag\":\"WSS\",\"description\":\"Subscribe to verbose open orders information including failed post-only orders\",\"href\":\"/exchange/api-reference/futures-websocket/open_orders_verbose\"},{\"title\":\"Open Positions\",\"tag\":\"WSS\",\"description\":\"Subscribe to open positions for your account\",\"href\":\"/exchange/api-reference/futures-websocket/open_position\"},{\"title\":\"Account Log\",\"tag\":\"WSS\",\"description\":\"Subscribe to account log information\",\"href\":\"/exchange/api-reference/futures-websocket/account_log\"},{\"title\":\"Notifications\",\"tag\":\"WSS\",\"description\":\"Subscribe to notifications for your account\",\"href\":\"/exchange/api-reference/futures-websocket/notifications\"}]},{\"group\":\"Authentication\",\"public\":true,\"pages\":[{\"title\":\"Challenge\",\"tag\":\"WSS\",\"description\":\"Request a challenge for user authentication handshake\",\"href\":\"/exchange/api-reference/futures-websocket/challenge\"}]}]},{\"dropdown\":\"Unified FIX\",\"icon\":\"terminal\",\"pages\":[{\"title\":\"Unified FIX\",\"sidebarTitle\":\"Unified FIX\",\"description\":\"FIX 4.4 reference for Spot and Derivatives — message types, session establishment, and endpoint mapping\",\"public\":true,\"href\":\"/exchange/api-reference/unified-fix\"},{\"group\":\"Trading\",\"public\":true,\"pages\":[{\"title\":\"New Order Single\",\"tag\":\"FIX\",\"description\":\"Submit a new order via FIX\",\"href\":\"/exchange/api-reference/unified-fix/nos\"},{\"title\":\"Order Cancel Request\",\"sidebarTitle\":\"Cancel Order\",\"tag\":\"FIX\",\"description\":\"Cancel a single order via FIX\",\"href\":\"/exchange/api-reference/unified-fix/ocr\"},{\"title\":\"Order Cancel Replace Request\",\"sidebarTitle\":\"Cancel Replace\",\"tag\":\"FIX\",\"description\":\"Amend a working order via FIX (Spot only)\",\"href\":\"/exchange/api-reference/unified-fix/ocrr\"},{\"title\":\"Order Status Request\",\"sidebarTitle\":\"Order Status\",\"tag\":\"FIX\",\"description\":\"Request current order status via FIX (Spot only)\",\"href\":\"/exchange/api-reference/unified-fix/osr\"},{\"title\":\"Order Mass Cancel Request\",\"sidebarTitle\":\"Mass Cancel\",\"tag\":\"FIX\",\"description\":\"Cancel all open orders via FIX\",\"href\":\"/exchange/api-reference/unified-fix/omcr\"},{\"title\":\"Execution Report\",\"tag\":\"FIX\",\"description\":\"Order responses and fill notifications via FIX\",\"href\":\"/exchange/api-reference/unified-fix/er\"}]},{\"group\":\"Market Data\",\"public\":true,\"pages\":[{\"title\":\"Instrument List Request\",\"sidebarTitle\":\"Instrument List Req\",\"tag\":\"FIX\",\"description\":\"Request a list of available instruments via FIX\",\"href\":\"/exchange/api-reference/unified-fix/slr\"},{\"title\":\"Instrument List\",\"tag\":\"FIX\",\"description\":\"Instrument parameters and status response via FIX\",\"href\":\"/exchange/api-reference/unified-fix/sl\"},{\"title\":\"Market Data Request\",\"tag\":\"FIX\",\"description\":\"Subscribe to market data streams via FIX\",\"href\":\"/exchange/api-reference/unified-fix/mdr\"},{\"title\":\"Market Data Request Reject\",\"sidebarTitle\":\"MD Request Reject\",\"tag\":\"FIX\",\"description\":\"Rejection of a market data subscription request via FIX\",\"href\":\"/exchange/api-reference/unified-fix/mdrr\"},{\"title\":\"Market Data Snapshot Full Refresh\",\"sidebarTitle\":\"MD Snapshot Full Refresh\",\"tag\":\"FIX\",\"description\":\"Full order book snapshot via FIX\",\"href\":\"/exchange/api-reference/unified-fix/mdsfr\"},{\"title\":\"Market Data Incremental Refresh\",\"sidebarTitle\":\"MD Incremental Refresh\",\"tag\":\"FIX\",\"description\":\"Incremental order book and trade updates via FIX\",\"href\":\"/exchange/api-reference/unified-fix/mdir\"},{\"title\":\"Trading Session Status Request\",\"sidebarTitle\":\"Session Status Request\",\"tag\":\"FIX\",\"description\":\"Request trading session status via FIX (Spot only)\",\"href\":\"/exchange/api-reference/unified-fix/tssr\"},{\"title\":\"Trading Session Status\",\"sidebarTitle\":\"Session Status\",\"tag\":\"FIX\",\"description\":\"Trading session status response via FIX (Spot only)\",\"href\":\"/exchange/api-reference/unified-fix/tss\"}]},{\"group\":\"Session\",\"public\":true,\"pages\":[{\"title\":\"Header \u0026 Trailer\",\"tag\":\"FIX\",\"description\":\"Standard FIX message header and trailer fields\",\"href\":\"/exchange/api-reference/unified-fix/header-trailer\"},{\"title\":\"Logon\",\"tag\":\"FIX\",\"description\":\"Authenticate and establish a FIX session\",\"href\":\"/exchange/api-reference/unified-fix/logon\"},{\"title\":\"Logout\",\"tag\":\"FIX\",\"description\":\"Terminate a FIX session\",\"href\":\"/exchange/api-reference/unified-fix/logout\"},{\"title\":\"Resend Request\",\"tag\":\"FIX\",\"description\":\"Request retransmission of messages when a sequence gap is detected\",\"href\":\"/exchange/api-reference/unified-fix/resend-request\"},{\"title\":\"Reject - Session Level\",\"sidebarTitle\":\"Session Reject\",\"tag\":\"FIX\",\"description\":\"Session level message rejection via FIX\",\"href\":\"/exchange/api-reference/unified-fix/reject-session\"},{\"title\":\"Reject - Business Level\",\"sidebarTitle\":\"Business Reject\",\"tag\":\"FIX\",\"description\":\"Business level message rejection via FIX\",\"href\":\"/exchange/api-reference/unified-fix/reject-business\"},{\"title\":\"Sequence Reset\",\"tag\":\"FIX\",\"description\":\"Reset message sequence numbers via FIX\",\"href\":\"/exchange/api-reference/unified-fix/sequence-reset\"}]}]}]},{\"tab\":\"Changelog\",\"pages\":[{\"title\":\"Release notes\",\"description\":\"A history of changes to Kraken's Exchange APIs\",\"mode\":\"center\",\"public\":true,\"href\":\"/exchange/changelog\"}]}]},{\"product\":\"Institutional\",\"tabs\":[{\"tab\":\"Guides\",\"groups\":[{\"group\":\"Getting started\",\"public\":true,\"pages\":[{\"title\":\"Institutional overview\",\"description\":\"OTC trading, custody, and prime brokerage APIs — designed for institutions managing large positions or client assets\",\"href\":\"/institutional/guides/overview\"}]},{\"group\":\"Authentication\",\"public\":true,\"pages\":[{\"title\":\"Custody REST Authentication\",\"description\":\"How to authenticate API requests to the Custody REST API using API keys, signatures, and nonces.\",\"href\":\"/institutional/guides/custody-rest-auth\"},{\"title\":\"Prime WebSocket Authentication\",\"description\":\"How to authenticate WebSocket connections to the Kraken Prime API using HMAC-SHA256 signed headers.\",\"href\":\"/institutional/guides/prime-websocket-auth\"}]}]},{\"tab\":\"API Reference\",\"dropdowns\":[{\"dropdown\":\"Overview\",\"icon\":\"compass\",\"pages\":[{\"title\":\"Institutional API reference\",\"sidebarTitle\":\"Overview\",\"description\":\"OTC, Custody, and Prime — pick the service and protocol for your workflow\",\"public\":true,\"href\":\"/institutional/api-reference/overview\"}]},{\"dropdown\":\"Custody REST\",\"icon\":\"code\",\"pages\":[{\"title\":\"Custody REST\",\"description\":\"Kraken Custody REST API reference\",\"public\":true,\"href\":\"/institutional/api-reference/custody-rest\"},{\"group\":\"Portfolios\",\"public\":true,\"hidden\":true,\"pages\":[{\"title\":\"List vaults\",\"description\":\"Retrieve all vaults within the custody domain.\",\"deprecated\":null,\"version\":null,\"openapi\":\"/openapi/custody-rest.yaml post /0/private/ListCustodyVaults\",\"href\":\"/api-reference/portfolios/list-vaults\",\"autogeneratedByOpenApi\":true},{\"title\":\"Get vault information by id\",\"description\":\"Retrieve information and balances for a specific vault.\",\"deprecated\":null,\"version\":null,\"openapi\":\"/openapi/custody-rest.yaml post /0/private/GetCustodyVault\",\"href\":\"/api-reference/portfolios/get-vault-information-by-id\",\"autogeneratedByOpenApi\":true},{\"title\":\"Get deposit methods\",\"description\":\"Retrieve the available deposit funding methods for depositing a specific asset. The deposit method is required to retrieve deposit addresses using the [Get Deposit Addresses API](/docs/custody-api/deposit-addresses).\",\"deprecated\":null,\"version\":null,\"openapi\":\"/openapi/custody-rest.yaml post /0/private/DepositMethods\",\"href\":\"/api-reference/portfolios/get-deposit-methods\",\"autogeneratedByOpenApi\":true},{\"title\":\"Get deposit addresses\",\"description\":\"Retrieve (or generate a new) deposit addresses for a particular asset and funding method. Use the [Get Deposit Methods API](/docs/custody-api/deposit-methods) to identify the appropriate deposit method.\",\"deprecated\":null,\"version\":null,\"openapi\":\"/openapi/custody-rest.yaml post /0/private/DepositAddresses\",\"href\":\"/api-reference/portfolios/get-deposit-addresses\",\"autogeneratedByOpenApi\":true},{\"title\":\"Get custody balance\",\"description\":\"Retrieve the balance for each asset held in the specified vault.\",\"deprecated\":null,\"version\":null,\"openapi\":\"/openapi/custody-rest.yaml post /0/private/GetCustodyBalance\",\"href\":\"/api-reference/portfolios/get-custody-balance\",\"autogeneratedByOpenApi\":true},{\"title\":\"List custody transactions\",\"description\":\"Retrieve the transaction history for a specified vault.\",\"deprecated\":null,\"version\":null,\"openapi\":\"/openapi/custody-rest.yaml post /0/private/ListCustodyTransactions\",\"href\":\"/api-reference/portfolios/list-custody-transactions\",\"autogeneratedByOpenApi\":true},{\"title\":\"Get transaction by id\",\"description\":\"Get transaction by id\",\"deprecated\":null,\"version\":null,\"openapi\":\"/openapi/custody-rest.yaml post /0/private/GetCustodyTransaction\",\"href\":\"/api-reference/portfolios/get-transaction-by-id\",\"autogeneratedByOpenApi\":true}]},{\"group\":\"Transfers\",\"public\":true,\"hidden\":true,\"pages\":[{\"title\":\"Get withdraw methods\",\"description\":\"Retrieve a list of withdrawal methods available for a specified vault.\",\"deprecated\":null,\"version\":null,\"openapi\":\"/openapi/custody-rest.yaml post /0/private/WithdrawMethods\",\"href\":\"/api-reference/transfers/get-withdraw-methods\",\"autogeneratedByOpenApi\":true},{\"title\":\"Get withdraw addresses\",\"description\":\"Retrieve a list of withdrawal addresses for a specified vault.\",\"deprecated\":null,\"version\":null,\"openapi\":\"/openapi/custody-rest.yaml post /0/private/WithdrawAddresses\",\"href\":\"/api-reference/transfers/get-withdraw-addresses\",\"autogeneratedByOpenApi\":true}]},{\"group\":\"Tasks\",\"public\":true,\"hidden\":true,\"pages\":[{\"title\":\"List tasks\",\"description\":\"Retrieve review tasks that match the specified filter criteria.\",\"deprecated\":null,\"version\":null,\"openapi\":\"/openapi/custody-rest.yaml post /0/private/ListCustodyTasks\",\"href\":\"/api-reference/tasks/list-tasks\",\"autogeneratedByOpenApi\":true},{\"title\":\"Get task by id\",\"description\":\"Retrieve details for a specific task.\",\"deprecated\":null,\"version\":null,\"openapi\":\"/openapi/custody-rest.yaml post /0/private/GetCustodyTask\",\"href\":\"/api-reference/tasks/get-task-by-id\",\"autogeneratedByOpenApi\":true},{\"title\":\"List activities\",\"description\":\"Retrieve all activities that match the specified filter criteria.\",\"deprecated\":null,\"version\":null,\"openapi\":\"/openapi/custody-rest.yaml post /0/private/ListCustodyActivities\",\"href\":\"/api-reference/tasks/list-activities\",\"autogeneratedByOpenApi\":true},{\"title\":\"Get activity by id\",\"description\":\"Retrieve details for a specific task activity.\",\"deprecated\":null,\"version\":null,\"openapi\":\"/openapi/custody-rest.yaml post /0/private/GetCustodyActivity\",\"href\":\"/api-reference/tasks/get-activity-by-id\",\"autogeneratedByOpenApi\":true}]},{\"group\":\"Assets (v0)\",\"public\":true,\"pages\":[{\"title\":\"List assets\",\"description\":\"Lists custody assets that support inbound funding via on-chain deposit or spot-to-vault transfer. Withdraw-only assets are omitted.\\n\\nEach entry includes the currency code, display metadata, network, and supported actions (`deposit`, `withdraw`, `transfer_to_spot`, `transfer_to_vault`, `stake`).\\n\\nNo authentication is required.\\n\\n**Rate limit:** 200 requests per 30 seconds per IP.\",\"deprecated\":null,\"version\":null,\"openapi\":\"/openapi/insto-custody-rest.yaml get /v0/insto/custody/assets\",\"href\":\"/api-reference/custody-external-api/list-assets\",\"autogeneratedByOpenApi\":true}]},{\"group\":\"Organizations (v0)\",\"public\":true,\"pages\":[{\"title\":\"List organizations\",\"description\":\"Returns the organizations the authenticated user belongs to. Each entry carries the organization identifier, display name, and lifecycle status.\\n\\n**Rate limit:** 200 requests per 30 seconds per IP.\",\"deprecated\":null,\"version\":null,\"openapi\":\"/openapi/insto-custody-rest.yaml get /v0/insto/custody/organizations\",\"href\":\"/api-reference/custody-external-api/list-organizations\",\"autogeneratedByOpenApi\":true},{\"title\":\"List balances\",\"description\":\"Returns the aggregated balance for an organization across all of its vaults, valued in the requested quote currency. The response breaks the total down into spot, staked, and pledged components.\\n\\n**Rate limit:** 200 requests per 30 seconds per IP.\",\"deprecated\":null,\"version\":null,\"openapi\":\"/openapi/insto-custody-rest.yaml get /v0/insto/custody/organizations/{org_iiban}/balances\",\"href\":\"/api-reference/custody-external-api/list-balances\",\"autogeneratedByOpenApi\":true}]},{\"group\":\"Vaults (v0)\",\"public\":true,\"pages\":[{\"title\":\"List vaults\",\"description\":\"Returns the vaults the authenticated user can access within an organization, each valued in the quote asset. Initiator and Reviewer API users see only the vaults they are a member of.\\n\\n**Rate limit:** 200 requests per 30 seconds per IP.\",\"deprecated\":null,\"version\":null,\"openapi\":\"/openapi/insto-custody-rest.yaml get /v0/insto/custody/vaults\",\"href\":\"/api-reference/custody-external-api/list-vaults\",\"autogeneratedByOpenApi\":true},{\"title\":\"Get vault balance\",\"description\":\"Returns the total balance for a vault valued in the requested quote currency. The response includes the 24-hour balance change and any assets for which a quote rate was unavailable.\\n\\n**Rate limit:** 200 requests per 30 seconds per IP.\",\"deprecated\":null,\"version\":null,\"openapi\":\"/openapi/insto-custody-rest.yaml get /v0/insto/custody/vaults/{vault_id}/balances\",\"href\":\"/api-reference/custody-external-api/get-vault-balance\",\"autogeneratedByOpenApi\":true},{\"title\":\"List vault asset balances\",\"description\":\"Returns per-asset balances for a vault, including spot, hold, available, staked, and pledged components for each asset. Each row includes asset metadata and optional quote-currency valuations. Use `quote_asset` to select the valuation currency (defaults to USD). Numeric strings are always returned at full upstream precision.\\n\\n**Rate limit:** 200 requests per 30 seconds per IP.\",\"deprecated\":null,\"version\":null,\"openapi\":\"/openapi/insto-custody-rest.yaml get /v0/insto/custody/vaults/{vault_id}/assets/balances\",\"href\":\"/api-reference/custody-external-api/list-vault-asset-balances\",\"autogeneratedByOpenApi\":true}]},{\"group\":\"Deposits (v0)\",\"public\":true,\"pages\":[{\"title\":\"List deposit methods\",\"description\":\"Returns the deposit methods available for the vault. Each entry carries the method identifier, fee, minimum, disabled flag, and the network metadata for the underlying chain. Filter by `asset` and `asset_class` together to limit results to a single asset.\\n\\n**Rate limit:** 200 requests per 30 seconds per IP.\",\"deprecated\":null,\"version\":null,\"openapi\":\"/openapi/insto-custody-rest.yaml get /v0/insto/custody/vaults/{vault_id}/deposit-methods\",\"href\":\"/api-reference/custody-external-api/list-deposit-methods\",\"autogeneratedByOpenApi\":true},{\"title\":\"List deposit addresses\",\"description\":\"Returns existing deposit addresses for the vault and deposit method. Each entry carries the address, optional routing fields like `tag` and `memo`, deposit fee, minimum and maximum amounts, expiration time (RFC 3339 UTC), and a flag indicating whether the caller may generate another address. The list is empty when no address has been generated yet.\\n\\n**Rate limit:** 200 requests per 30 seconds per IP.\",\"deprecated\":null,\"version\":null,\"sidebarTitle\":\"List deposit addresses\",\"openapi\":\"/openapi/insto-custody-rest.yaml get /v0/insto/custody/vaults/{vault_id}/deposit-methods/{method_id}/addresses\",\"href\":\"/api-reference/custody-external-api/list-deposit-addresses\",\"autogeneratedByOpenApi\":true},{\"title\":\"Create address\",\"description\":\"Generates a new deposit address for the vault and deposit method. The response carries the new address along with deposit fee, minimum and maximum amounts, expiration time (RFC 3339 UTC), and the asset and asset class the method belongs to. The request fails with `TooManyAddresses` when the maximum number of addresses for the method has been reached.\\n\\n**Rate limit:** 200 requests per 30 seconds per IP.\",\"deprecated\":null,\"version\":null,\"openapi\":\"/openapi/insto-custody-rest.yaml post /v0/insto/custody/vaults/{vault_id}/deposit-methods/{method_id}/addresses\",\"href\":\"/api-reference/custody-external-api/create-address\",\"autogeneratedByOpenApi\":true},{\"title\":\"Get deposit info\",\"description\":\"Returns the deposit methods available for a specific asset in a vault. Each entry carries the funding method identifier, fees, minimums, and the underlying network metadata needed to display a deposit screen.\\n\\n**Rate limit:** 200 requests per 30 seconds per IP.\",\"deprecated\":null,\"version\":null,\"openapi\":\"/openapi/insto-custody-rest.yaml get /v0/insto/custody/vaults/{vault_id}/deposits/info\",\"href\":\"/api-reference/custody-external-api/get-deposit-info\",\"autogeneratedByOpenApi\":true}]},{\"group\":\"Withdrawals (v0)\",\"public\":true,\"pages\":[{\"title\":\"List whitelist addresses\",\"description\":\"Returns the whitelisted withdrawal addresses for a vault, optionally filtered by asset.\\n\\n**Rate limit:** 200 requests per 30 seconds per IP.\",\"deprecated\":null,\"version\":null,\"sidebarTitle\":\"List whitelist addresses\",\"openapi\":\"/openapi/insto-custody-rest.yaml get /v0/insto/custody/vaults/{vault_id}/whitelist/addresses\",\"href\":\"/api-reference/custody-external-api/list-whitelist-addresses\",\"autogeneratedByOpenApi\":true},{\"title\":\"List withdrawal methods\",\"description\":\"Returns the withdrawal methods available for the vault. Each entry carries the method identifier, fee and fee asset, minimum withdrawal amount, disabled flag, and the network metadata for the underlying chain. Filter by `asset` and `asset_class` together to limit results to a single asset.\\n\\n**Rate limit:** 200 requests per 30 seconds per IP.\",\"deprecated\":null,\"version\":null,\"openapi\":\"/openapi/insto-custody-rest.yaml get /v0/insto/custody/vaults/{vault_id}/withdrawal-methods\",\"href\":\"/api-reference/custody-external-api/list-withdrawal-methods\",\"autogeneratedByOpenApi\":true},{\"title\":\"Get withdrawal info\",\"description\":\"Returns withdrawal methods, fees, limits, and network metadata for a specific asset in a vault. Each entry carries the method identifier, fee structure, minimum and maximum amounts, and validation rules needed to display a withdrawal screen.\\n\\n**Rate limit:** 200 requests per 30 seconds per IP.\",\"deprecated\":null,\"version\":null,\"openapi\":\"/openapi/insto-custody-rest.yaml get /v0/insto/custody/vaults/{vault_id}/withdrawals/info\",\"href\":\"/api-reference/custody-external-api/get-withdrawal-info\",\"autogeneratedByOpenApi\":true},{\"title\":\"Create withdrawal fee quote\",\"description\":\"Generates a fee quote for a hypothetical withdrawal from the specified vault. Callers supply the asset and amount they intend to withdraw and receive back a `fee_quote_id` along with a set of fee tiers, each describing the fee charged at a given priority level. The returned `fee_quote_id` can then be passed as `fee_quote_id` on a `request_withdrawal` instruction to `POST /v0/insto/custody/tasks` to submit the actual withdrawal. Quotes are advisory and expire after a short window.\\n\\n**Rate limit:** 200 requests per 30 seconds per IP.\",\"deprecated\":null,\"version\":null,\"openapi\":\"/openapi/insto-custody-rest.yaml post /v0/insto/custody/vaults/{vault_id}/withdrawals/fee-quotes\",\"href\":\"/api-reference/custody-external-api/create-withdrawal-fee-quote\",\"autogeneratedByOpenApi\":true}]},{\"group\":\"Tasks (v0)\",\"public\":true,\"pages\":[{\"title\":\"List tasks\",\"description\":\"Returns a paginated list of custody tasks (approval requests) visible to the authenticated user, filtered by the supplied query parameters and ordered by the requested column. Multi-valued filters are OR-ed within a field and AND-ed across fields.\\n\\n**Rate limit:** 200 requests per 30 seconds per IP.\",\"deprecated\":null,\"version\":null,\"openapi\":\"/openapi/insto-custody-rest.yaml get /v0/insto/custody/tasks\",\"href\":\"/api-reference/custody-external-api/list-tasks\",\"autogeneratedByOpenApi\":true},{\"title\":\"Create task\",\"description\":\"Creates an approval task from one or more instructions. Each instruction describes a single change, such as a withdrawal, a sub-quorum update, or a user removal. The task is created in a pending state and its instructions take effect asynchronously once the task is approved. The response returns the task identifier and the identifier of the associated approval flow.\\n\\n**Rate limit:** 200 requests per 30 seconds per IP.\",\"deprecated\":null,\"version\":null,\"openapi\":\"/openapi/insto-custody-rest.yaml post /v0/insto/custody/tasks\",\"href\":\"/api-reference/custody-external-api/create-task\",\"autogeneratedByOpenApi\":true},{\"title\":\"Get task by id\",\"description\":\"Returns the full details of a single task, including its instructions, the activity timeline, and reviewer/quorum state. Available only to callers in the task's owning organization. Each task is exposed as a list of atomic instructions, where every entry describes a single change.\\n\\n**Rate limit:** 200 requests per 30 seconds per IP.\",\"deprecated\":null,\"version\":null,\"openapi\":\"/openapi/insto-custody-rest.yaml get /v0/insto/custody/tasks/{task_id}\",\"href\":\"/api-reference/custody-external-api/get-task-by-id\",\"autogeneratedByOpenApi\":true},{\"title\":\"Review task\",\"description\":\"Records the authenticated user's review decision on a task. The decision is `approve` or `deny`, with an optional comment. The caller must be an assigned reviewer and must not already have voted; if either condition fails the request is rejected with a `403`. The response returns the task's new lifecycle state after the decision is applied.\\n\\n**Rate limit:** 200 requests per 30 seconds per IP.\",\"deprecated\":null,\"version\":null,\"openapi\":\"/openapi/insto-custody-rest.yaml post /v0/insto/custody/tasks/{task_id}/review\",\"href\":\"/api-reference/custody-external-api/review-task\",\"autogeneratedByOpenApi\":true}]},{\"group\":\"Transactions (v0)\",\"public\":true,\"pages\":[{\"title\":\"List transactions\",\"description\":\"Returns a paginated list of transactions for the given vault. Filter by transaction type, asset, and sort order. Use `cursor` from a prior response to fetch subsequent pages.\\n\\n**Rate limit:** 200 requests per 30 seconds per IP.\",\"deprecated\":null,\"version\":null,\"openapi\":\"/openapi/insto-custody-rest.yaml get /v0/insto/custody/vaults/{vault_id}/transactions\",\"href\":\"/api-reference/custody-external-api/list-transactions\",\"autogeneratedByOpenApi\":true},{\"title\":\"Get transaction\",\"description\":\"Returns a single transaction for the given vault. Available only to callers with access to the vault.\\n\\n**Rate limit:** 200 requests per 30 seconds per IP.\",\"deprecated\":null,\"version\":null,\"openapi\":\"/openapi/insto-custody-rest.yaml get /v0/insto/custody/vaults/{vault_id}/transactions/{transaction_id}\",\"href\":\"/api-reference/custody-external-api/get-transaction\",\"autogeneratedByOpenApi\":true}]}]},{\"dropdown\":\"OTC REST\",\"icon\":\"code\",\"pages\":[{\"title\":\"OTC REST\",\"description\":\"Kraken OTC REST API reference\",\"public\":true,\"href\":\"/institutional/api-reference/otc-rest\"},{\"group\":\"Quotes\",\"public\":true,\"pages\":[{\"title\":\"Create OTC Quote\",\"description\":\"Creates a new OTC request for quote.\\n\\n**API Key Permissions Required:** `Orders and trades - Create \u0026 modify orders`\\n\",\"deprecated\":null,\"version\":null,\"openapi\":\"/openapi/otc-rest.yaml post /private/CreateOtcQuoteRequest\",\"href\":\"/api-reference/quotes/create-otc-quote\",\"autogeneratedByOpenApi\":true},{\"title\":\"Update OTC Quote\",\"description\":\"Accepts or rejects an OTC quote.\\n\\n**API Key Permissions Required:** `Orders and trades - Create \u0026 modify orders`\\n\",\"deprecated\":null,\"version\":null,\"openapi\":\"/openapi/otc-rest.yaml post /private/UpdateOtcQuote\",\"href\":\"/api-reference/quotes/update-otc-quote\",\"autogeneratedByOpenApi\":true},{\"title\":\"Get OTC Pairs\",\"description\":\"Retrieves the list of OTC trading pairs.\\n\\n**API Key Permissions Required:** `Funds permissions - Query` and `Funds permissions - Deposit`\\n\",\"deprecated\":null,\"version\":null,\"openapi\":\"/openapi/otc-rest.yaml post /private/GetOtcPairs\",\"href\":\"/api-reference/quotes/get-otc-pairs\",\"autogeneratedByOpenApi\":true},{\"title\":\"Get OTC Active Quotes\",\"description\":\"Retrieves a list of active OTC quotes.\\n\\n**API Key Permissions Required:** `Orders and trades - Query open orders \u0026 trades`\\n\",\"deprecated\":null,\"version\":null,\"openapi\":\"/openapi/otc-rest.yaml post /private/GetOtcActiveQuotes\",\"href\":\"/api-reference/quotes/get-otc-active-quotes\",\"autogeneratedByOpenApi\":true},{\"title\":\"Get OTC Historical Quotes\",\"description\":\"Retrieves OTC quotes history.\\n\\n**API Key Permissions Required:** `Orders and trades - Query open orders \u0026 trades`\\n\",\"deprecated\":null,\"version\":null,\"openapi\":\"/openapi/otc-rest.yaml post /private/GetOtcHistoricalQuotes\",\"href\":\"/api-reference/quotes/get-otc-historical-quotes\",\"autogeneratedByOpenApi\":true},{\"title\":\"Get OTC Exposures\",\"description\":\"Retrieves the max and used OTC exposures.\\n\\n**API Key Permissions Required:** `Orders and trades - Query open orders \u0026 trades`\\n\",\"deprecated\":null,\"version\":null,\"openapi\":\"/openapi/otc-rest.yaml post /private/GetOtcExposures\",\"href\":\"/api-reference/quotes/get-otc-exposures\",\"autogeneratedByOpenApi\":true},{\"title\":\"Check OTC Eligibility\",\"description\":\"Retrieves the client permissions for the OTC Portal.\\n\\n**API Key Permissions Required:** `Funds permissions - Query` and `Funds permissions - Deposit`\\n\",\"deprecated\":null,\"version\":null,\"openapi\":\"/openapi/otc-rest.yaml post /private/CheckOtcClient\",\"href\":\"/api-reference/quotes/check-otc-eligibility\",\"autogeneratedByOpenApi\":true}]}]},{\"dropdown\":\"Prime REST\",\"icon\":\"code\",\"pages\":[{\"title\":\"Prime REST\",\"sidebarTitle\":\"Prime REST\",\"description\":\"Programmatic access to Kraken Prime — API-user management, key lifecycle, and settlement\",\"public\":true,\"href\":\"/institutional/api-reference/prime-rest\"},{\"group\":\"API Users\",\"public\":true,\"pages\":[{\"title\":\"Create Prime API User\",\"description\":\"Creates a new Prime API user with the specified role. Valid roles are `Viewer` and `Trader`.\\n\",\"deprecated\":null,\"version\":null,\"openapi\":\"/openapi/prime-rest.yaml post /0/private/CreatePrimeApiUser\",\"href\":\"/api-reference/api-users/create-prime-api-user\",\"autogeneratedByOpenApi\":true},{\"title\":\"Get Prime API User\",\"description\":\"Retrieves details of a specific Prime API user by ID.\\n\",\"deprecated\":null,\"version\":null,\"openapi\":\"/openapi/prime-rest.yaml post /0/private/GetPrimeApiUser\",\"href\":\"/api-reference/api-users/get-prime-api-user\",\"autogeneratedByOpenApi\":true},{\"title\":\"List Prime API Users\",\"description\":\"Retrieves a list of all Prime API users for the account.\\n\",\"deprecated\":null,\"version\":null,\"openapi\":\"/openapi/prime-rest.yaml post /0/private/ListPrimeApiUsers\",\"href\":\"/api-reference/api-users/list-prime-api-users\",\"autogeneratedByOpenApi\":true},{\"title\":\"Update Prime API User\",\"description\":\"Updates the name or status of a Prime API user.\\n\",\"deprecated\":null,\"version\":null,\"openapi\":\"/openapi/prime-rest.yaml post /0/private/UpdatePrimeApiUser\",\"href\":\"/api-reference/api-users/update-prime-api-user\",\"autogeneratedByOpenApi\":true},{\"title\":\"Update Prime API User Roles\",\"description\":\"Updates the role assigned to a Prime API user. Valid roles are `Viewer` and `Trader`.\\n\",\"deprecated\":null,\"version\":null,\"openapi\":\"/openapi/prime-rest.yaml post /0/private/UpdatePrimeApiUserRoles\",\"href\":\"/api-reference/api-users/update-prime-api-user-roles\",\"autogeneratedByOpenApi\":true}]},{\"group\":\"API User Keys\",\"public\":true,\"pages\":[{\"title\":\"Create Prime API User Key\",\"description\":\"Creates a new API key for a Prime API user. The API secret is only returned in this response and cannot be retrieved later.\\n\",\"deprecated\":null,\"version\":null,\"openapi\":\"/openapi/prime-rest.yaml post /0/private/CreatePrimeApiUserKey\",\"href\":\"/api-reference/api-user-keys/create-prime-api-user-key\",\"autogeneratedByOpenApi\":true},{\"title\":\"List Prime API User Keys\",\"description\":\"Retrieves all API keys for a specific Prime API user. The API secret is not included in the response.\\n\",\"deprecated\":null,\"version\":null,\"openapi\":\"/openapi/prime-rest.yaml post /0/private/ListPrimeApiUserKeys\",\"href\":\"/api-reference/api-user-keys/list-prime-api-user-keys\",\"autogeneratedByOpenApi\":true},{\"title\":\"Update Prime API User Key\",\"description\":\"Updates the whitelisted IPs for a Prime API user key.\\n\",\"deprecated\":null,\"version\":null,\"openapi\":\"/openapi/prime-rest.yaml post /0/private/UpdatePrimeApiUserKey\",\"href\":\"/api-reference/api-user-keys/update-prime-api-user-key\",\"autogeneratedByOpenApi\":true},{\"title\":\"Delete Prime API User Key\",\"description\":\"Permanently deletes an API key for a Prime API user. This action cannot be undone.\\n\",\"deprecated\":null,\"version\":null,\"openapi\":\"/openapi/prime-rest.yaml post /0/private/DeletePrimeApiUserKey\",\"href\":\"/api-reference/api-user-keys/delete-prime-api-user-key\",\"autogeneratedByOpenApi\":true}]},{\"group\":\"Settlement\",\"public\":true,\"pages\":[{\"title\":\"Create Prime Settlement Batch\",\"description\":\"Creates a new Prime settlement batch from pending unsettled trades. Only one active batch per `asset_kind` can exist at a time.\\n\\nOptionally pass `asset_kind` in the request body to select which trades to include: `currency` (fiat and cryptocurrency positions; default) or `tokenized_equity` (tokenized equity positions).\\n\\nThe response includes `trade_ids` — the trade IDs captured in the batch.\\n\\n**API Key Permissions Required:** `Orders and trades - Create \u0026 modify orders`\\n\",\"deprecated\":null,\"version\":null,\"openapi\":\"/openapi/prime-rest.yaml post /0/private/CreatePrimeSettlementBatch\",\"href\":\"/api-reference/settlement/create-prime-settlement-batch\",\"autogeneratedByOpenApi\":true},{\"title\":\"Get Prime Settlement Batch\",\"description\":\"Retrieves a specific Prime settlement batch by its ID, including all legs, their current settlement status,\\nexternal transfers that have settled each leg, and the trade IDs in the batch.\\n\\n**API Key Permissions Required:** `Orders and trades - Query open orders \u0026 trades`\\n\",\"deprecated\":null,\"version\":null,\"openapi\":\"/openapi/prime-rest.yaml post /0/private/GetPrimeSettlementBatch\",\"href\":\"/api-reference/settlement/get-prime-settlement-batch\",\"autogeneratedByOpenApi\":true},{\"title\":\"List Prime Settlement Batches\",\"description\":\"Retrieves a list of Prime settlement batches, optionally filtered by status and time range. Results are sorted by creation time, most recent first.\\n\\n**API Key Permissions Required:** `Orders and trades - Query open orders \u0026 trades`\\n\",\"deprecated\":null,\"version\":null,\"openapi\":\"/openapi/prime-rest.yaml post /0/private/ListPrimeSettlementBatches\",\"href\":\"/api-reference/settlement/list-prime-settlement-batches\",\"autogeneratedByOpenApi\":true},{\"title\":\"Settle Prime Settlement Batch Asset\",\"description\":\"Initiates settlement of a specific asset leg within a Prime settlement batch. The batch must be confirmed and the leg must be eligible for settlement (check `can_settle` on the leg).\\n\\n**API Key Permissions Required:** `Orders and trades - Create \u0026 modify orders`\\n\",\"deprecated\":null,\"version\":null,\"openapi\":\"/openapi/prime-rest.yaml post /0/private/SettlePrimeSettlementBatchAsset\",\"href\":\"/api-reference/settlement/settle-prime-settlement-batch-asset\",\"autogeneratedByOpenApi\":true}]}]},{\"dropdown\":\"Prime FIX\",\"icon\":\"terminal\",\"groups\":[{\"group\":\"Session\",\"public\":true,\"pages\":[{\"title\":\"Logon\",\"description\":\"Authenticate and establish a FIX session using HMAC SHA-256 signature-based authentication.\",\"href\":\"/institutional/api-reference/prime-fix/logon\"},{\"title\":\"Logout\",\"description\":\"FIX message used to initiate or confirm the termination of a FIX session.\",\"href\":\"/institutional/api-reference/prime-fix/logout\"},{\"title\":\"Header \u0026 Trailer\",\"description\":\"Standard FIX message header and trailer fields required in every FIX message.\",\"sidebarTitle\":\"Header \u0026 Trailer\",\"href\":\"/institutional/api-reference/prime-fix/header-trailer\"},{\"title\":\"Heartbeat\",\"description\":\"FIX message used to maintain session connectivity and confirm the application is functioning normally.\",\"href\":\"/institutional/api-reference/prime-fix/heartbeat\"},{\"title\":\"Test Request\",\"description\":\"FIX message used to force a Heartbeat from the counterparty.\",\"href\":\"/institutional/api-reference/prime-fix/test-request\"},{\"title\":\"Resend Request\",\"description\":\"FIX message used to request retransmission of messages when a sequence gap is detected.\",\"href\":\"/institutional/api-reference/prime-fix/resend-request\"},{\"title\":\"Sequence Reset\",\"description\":\"FIX message used to reset sequence numbering or indicate that a range of sequence numbers will not be transmitted.\",\"href\":\"/institutional/api-reference/prime-fix/sequence-reset\"},{\"title\":\"Session Reject\",\"description\":\"FIX message used to reject a received message at the session level due to protocol violations.\",\"href\":\"/institutional/api-reference/prime-fix/session-reject\"}]},{\"group\":\"Order Management\",\"public\":true,\"pages\":[{\"title\":\"New Order Single\",\"description\":\"Submit a new order to the Kraken order book via FIX.\",\"href\":\"/institutional/api-reference/prime-fix/nos\"},{\"title\":\"Order Cancel Request\",\"description\":\"Cancel an existing order via FIX.\",\"href\":\"/institutional/api-reference/prime-fix/ocr\"},{\"title\":\"Order Cancel Replace Request\",\"description\":\"Amend the price, quantity, or other attributes of an existing FIX order.\",\"sidebarTitle\":\"Order Cancel Replace\",\"href\":\"/institutional/api-reference/prime-fix/ocrr\"},{\"title\":\"Order Cancel Reject\",\"description\":\"Response message used to reject invalid order cancel or cancel/replace requests.\",\"sidebarTitle\":\"Order Cancel Reject\",\"href\":\"/institutional/api-reference/prime-fix/ocrej\"},{\"title\":\"Execution Report\",\"description\":\"FIX message used to acknowledge or reject orders, and to relay order status and fill updates.\",\"href\":\"/institutional/api-reference/prime-fix/er\"}]},{\"group\":\"Security List\",\"public\":true,\"pages\":[{\"title\":\"Security List\",\"description\":\"FIX response message returning the list of securities matching a Security List Request.\",\"href\":\"/institutional/api-reference/prime-fix/sl\"},{\"title\":\"Security List Request\",\"description\":\"FIX message to request the list of securities available for trading.\",\"href\":\"/institutional/api-reference/prime-fix/slr\"}]},{\"group\":\"Market Data\",\"public\":true,\"pages\":[{\"title\":\"Market Data Request\",\"description\":\"FIX message to request market data for a specific symbol.\",\"href\":\"/institutional/api-reference/prime-fix/mdr\"},{\"title\":\"Market Data Request Reject\",\"description\":\"FIX message used to reject invalid market data requests.\",\"sidebarTitle\":\"Market Data Request Reject\",\"href\":\"/institutional/api-reference/prime-fix/mdrr\"},{\"title\":\"Market Data Snapshot Full Refresh\",\"description\":\"FIX message providing a complete refresh of market data for a requested symbol.\",\"sidebarTitle\":\"Market Data Snapshot\",\"href\":\"/institutional/api-reference/prime-fix/mdsfr\"}]}]},{\"dropdown\":\"Prime WebSocket\",\"icon\":\"bolt\",\"groups\":[{\"group\":\"Connection\",\"public\":true,\"pages\":[{\"title\":\"Authentication\",\"description\":\"Authenticate WebSocket connections to the Kraken Prime API using HMAC-SHA256 signed headers.\",\"href\":\"/institutional/api-reference/prime-websocket/authentication\"},{\"title\":\"Hello\",\"description\":\"Server-sent hello message on a successful WebSocket connection.\",\"href\":\"/institutional/api-reference/prime-websocket/hello\"},{\"title\":\"Ping\",\"description\":\"Optional client-initiated ping to verify connectivity; server responds with a Pong message.\",\"href\":\"/institutional/api-reference/prime-websocket/ping\"}]},{\"group\":\"Subscription Management\",\"public\":true,\"pages\":[{\"title\":\"Subscribe\",\"description\":\"Send a subscription request to begin a stream of data from the Prime WebSocket API.\",\"href\":\"/institutional/api-reference/prime-websocket/subscribe\"},{\"title\":\"Continue Paged Stream\",\"description\":\"Request the next page of data when a paged stream response includes a next field.\",\"href\":\"/institutional/api-reference/prime-websocket/page\"},{\"title\":\"Cancel Stream\",\"description\":\"Cancel an existing stream by request ID. The stream stops sending data; no response unless there is an error.\",\"href\":\"/institutional/api-reference/prime-websocket/cancel\"}]},{\"group\":\"Order Management\",\"public\":true,\"pages\":[{\"title\":\"New Order Single\",\"description\":\"Authenticated command to submit a new order against available liquidity or an open RFQ.\",\"sidebarTitle\":\"New Order Single\",\"href\":\"/institutional/api-reference/prime-websocket/new-order-single\"},{\"title\":\"Order Cancel Request\",\"description\":\"Authenticated command to cancel an open order.\",\"sidebarTitle\":\"Order Cancel Request\",\"href\":\"/institutional/api-reference/prime-websocket/order-cancel-request\"},{\"title\":\"Order Cancel Replace Request\",\"description\":\"Authenticated command to modify an open order's price, quantity, or strategy.\",\"sidebarTitle\":\"Order Cancel Replace\",\"href\":\"/institutional/api-reference/prime-websocket/order-cancel-replace-request\"},{\"title\":\"Order Control Request\",\"description\":\"Authenticated command to pause or resume an open order.\",\"sidebarTitle\":\"Order Control Request\",\"href\":\"/institutional/api-reference/prime-websocket/order-control-request\"},{\"title\":\"Order Updates\",\"description\":\"Authenticated channel for streaming real-time order status updates.\",\"sidebarTitle\":\"Order Updates\",\"href\":\"/institutional/api-reference/prime-websocket/order\"},{\"title\":\"Execution Report\",\"description\":\"Authenticated channel for streaming all order responses and lifecycle updates.\",\"sidebarTitle\":\"Execution Report\",\"href\":\"/institutional/api-reference/prime-websocket/execution-report\"}]},{\"group\":\"Market Data\",\"public\":true,\"pages\":[{\"title\":\"Security\",\"description\":\"Public channel for streaming the list of available securities and real-time updates to their properties.\",\"href\":\"/institutional/api-reference/prime-websocket/security\"},{\"title\":\"Market Data Snapshot\",\"description\":\"Public channel for streaming real-time bid/offer levels for a security.\",\"sidebarTitle\":\"Market Data Snapshot\",\"href\":\"/institutional/api-reference/prime-websocket/market-data-snapshot\"}]},{\"group\":\"Account\",\"public\":true,\"pages\":[{\"title\":\"Balance\",\"description\":\"Authenticated channel for streaming real-time account balance updates.\",\"href\":\"/institutional/api-reference/prime-websocket/balance\"},{\"title\":\"Trade\",\"description\":\"Authenticated channel for streaming real-time trade fill updates.\",\"href\":\"/institutional/api-reference/prime-websocket/trade\"},{\"title\":\"Exposure\",\"description\":\"Authenticated channel for streaming real-time credit utilization and exposure limit information.\",\"href\":\"/institutional/api-reference/prime-websocket/exposure\"},{\"title\":\"User\",\"description\":\"Authenticated channel for streaming updates for the current customer user.\",\"href\":\"/institutional/api-reference/prime-websocket/user\"},{\"title\":\"User Config\",\"description\":\"Authenticated command to update user configuration settings for the session user.\",\"sidebarTitle\":\"User Config\",\"href\":\"/institutional/api-reference/prime-websocket/user-config\"}]},{\"group\":\"RFQ\",\"public\":true,\"pages\":[{\"title\":\"Quote Request\",\"description\":\"Authenticated command to open a new RFQ and request a streaming quote.\",\"sidebarTitle\":\"Quote Request\",\"href\":\"/institutional/api-reference/prime-websocket/quote-request\"},{\"title\":\"Quote Updates\",\"description\":\"Authenticated channel for streaming real-time quote responses from RFQ requests.\",\"sidebarTitle\":\"Quote Updates\",\"href\":\"/institutional/api-reference/prime-websocket/quote\"},{\"title\":\"Quote Cancel Request\",\"description\":\"Authenticated command to cancel an open RFQ.\",\"sidebarTitle\":\"Quote Cancel Request\",\"href\":\"/institutional/api-reference/prime-websocket/quote-cancel-request\"}]},{\"group\":\"Reference Data\",\"public\":true,\"pages\":[{\"title\":\"Currency\",\"description\":\"Public channel for streaming available currencies used within trading.\",\"href\":\"/institutional/api-reference/prime-websocket/currency\"},{\"title\":\"Currency Conversion\",\"description\":\"Public channel for streaming real-time currency conversion rates.\",\"sidebarTitle\":\"Currency Conversion\",\"href\":\"/institutional/api-reference/prime-websocket/currency-conversion\"}]}]}]},{\"tab\":\"Changelog\",\"pages\":[{\"title\":\"Release notes\",\"description\":\"A history of changes to Kraken's Institutional APIs\",\"mode\":\"center\",\"public\":true,\"href\":\"/institutional/changelog\"}]}]},{\"product\":\"Pay\",\"tabs\":[{\"tab\":\"Guides\",\"groups\":[{\"group\":\"Pay\",\"public\":true,\"pages\":[{\"title\":\"Pay webhook notifications\",\"description\":\"Handle Kraken Pay webhook notifications for payment status changes using JWT verification with ES256.\",\"keywords\":[\"webhook\",\"kraken pay\",\"jwt\",\"es256\",\"payment status\",\"callback\",\"notification\"],\"sidebarTitle\":\"Pay webhooks\",\"href\":\"/pay/guides/pay-webhook\"}]}]},{\"tab\":\"API Reference\",\"dropdowns\":[{\"dropdown\":\"Pay REST\",\"icon\":\"code\",\"groups\":[{\"group\":\"Request\",\"public\":true,\"pages\":[{\"title\":\"Create a payment request\",\"description\":\"Create a payment request\\n\\n**API Key Permissions Required:** `Funds permissions - Deposit`\\n\",\"deprecated\":null,\"version\":null,\"openapi\":\"/openapi/pay-rest.yaml post /private/Pay/request/create\",\"href\":\"/api-reference/request/create-a-payment-request\",\"autogeneratedByOpenApi\":true},{\"title\":\"Cancel a payment request\",\"description\":\"Cancel a payment request\\n\\n**API Key Permissions Required:** `Funds permissions - Query`\\n\",\"deprecated\":null,\"version\":null,\"openapi\":\"/openapi/pay-rest.yaml post /private/Pay/request/cancel\",\"href\":\"/api-reference/request/cancel-a-payment-request\",\"autogeneratedByOpenApi\":true}]},{\"group\":\"Transfer\",\"public\":true,\"pages\":[{\"title\":\"Create a pay transfer\",\"description\":\"This method is asynchronous, your callback will be sent the `external_id` and the `status` when it reaches a final state.\\n\\n*